      "prompt": "This papercraft pop-up book prompt works for any product. <instruction> 1. Brand Deconstruction: Input a famous consumer brand/product/mascot. Deconstruct into 4 assets — The Mascot/Hero (iconic character or product shape), The Environment (idealized origin setting), The Typography (catchphrase + logo), The Consumer (target audience as secondary characters). 2. Container (Pop-Up Box): goal = 'Interactive Packaging' diorama photography. The base is the actual cardboard packaging box, lying flat, opened like a book; original branding/logos/info visible on the front edge. Setting: warm sunlit wooden kitchen/dining table. 3. Diorama (Paper Engineering): complex pop-up book art; everything erupting from the open box built from layered printed folded cardstock; visible tabs, creases, 'Pull' arrow mechanisms required. Background = layered paper landscape from the Environment (e.g. rising paper sun + cornfields). Foreground = the Mascot bursts forward as a large multi-layered paper cutout. Center = a giant stylized paper representation of the product. 4. Narrative Scale: smaller paper cutouts of Consumers interacting with the giant product; large curved paper banners across the top with the Slogan; small wooden-style paper signs with extra brand messaging. 5. Lighting & Atmosphere: sunny morning light, warm golden directional from top-left window, sharp distinct shadows behind paper layers emphasizing 3D pop-up depth; high fidelity cardboard thickness, matte printed ink, scissor-cut edges. Output: ONE image, 16:9, 3D render/macro photography, 'Nostalgic Papercraft' aesthetic, vibrant commercial colors. </instruction>",
      "prompt_ko": "어떤 제품이든 페이퍼크래프트 팝업북으로. [지시] 1.브랜드 해체: 유명 브랜드/제품/마스코트 입력→마스코트(히어로)·환경(기원)·타이포(슬로건)·소비자 4요소 추출. 2.컨테이너(팝업박스): '인터랙티브 패키징' 디오라마 사진. 실제 제품 패키지 박스가 책처럼 펼쳐져 평평히 누움, 로고·정보는 박스 앞면 가장자리에 보임. 따뜻한 햇살 나무 식탁. 3.디오라마(페이퍼 엔지니어링): 복잡한 팝업북 아트, 박스에서 솟는 모든 게 인쇄·접힌 카드스톡, 탭·접힘선·'당김' 화살표 필수. 배경=환경 기반 종이 풍경(떠오르는 종이 해+옥수수밭). 전경=마스코트가 큰 다층 종이 컷아웃으로 돌출. 중앙=거대 스타일화 종이 제품. 4.내러티브 스케일: 소비자 종이 컷아웃이 거대 제품과 상호작용, 상단 곡선 종이 배너에 슬로건, 작은 나무풍 종이 표지판. 5.조명: 맑은 아침 햇살(좌상단 창), 종이층 뒤 선명한 그림자로 3D 깊이, 골판지 두께·매트 잉크·가위 자른 엣지. 출력: 1장, 16:9, 3D렌더/매크로, 노스탤직 페이퍼크래프트, 비비드 커머셜 컬러.",
