      "prompt": "General Prompt: Generate a vertical 3:4 art poster, a fully completed and laid-out finished poster.\nThe theme is [Theme] — not ordinary ocean photography nor ordinary fish illustration, but a conceptual poster with strong emotional temperament, dreamlike feel, atmospheric vibe, design sensibility.\n[Core Visual] Center on [school of fish / jellyfish / tropical fish / glowing fish / translucent marine creatures / floating objects / sea-surface light] as the main subject, but heavily surreal — do not replicate realistically; transform into a striking artistic image. Incorporate: hazy mist, gradient seawater, floating particles, soft focus, light halos, subtle grain, blurred edges, dreamcore atmosphere, low-contrast background, ethereal negative space, floating composition.\n[Composition] Clear focal point; large negative space, off-center, floating layout, poster-style cropping, upper/lower layering, rhythmic density, depth contrast, single-side title, corner info. Like a genuine design poster, not a wallpaper.\n[Color & Atmosphere] Palette around [primary color: coral orange / misty pink / sea-salt blue / deep-sea black / neon purple / gray-green / amber gold]. Unified, soft, airy; subtle film grain, matte, slight print effect. Keywords: serene, ethereal, melancholic, healing, hazy, dreamy, surreal, poetic.\n[Text Layout] Complete typesetting in the image — Main title: [Main Title] / Subtitle: [short copy] / fine print [1/2/3]. Restrained sophisticated, no advertising vibe, no clutter. No real brand names, watermarks, garbled text, or dates.\n[Texture] High-end art-poster texture, soft-focus photo feel, dreamy ocean atmosphere, printed grain, modern design. Output: complete finished poster.",
      "gen_prompt": "General Prompt: Generate a vertical 3:4 art poster, a fully completed and laid-out finished poster.\nThe theme is [Theme] — not ordinary ocean photography nor ordinary fish illustration, but a conceptual poster with strong emotional temperament, dreamlike feel, atmospheric vibe, design sensibility.\n[Core Visual] Center on [school of fish / jellyfish / tropical fish / glowing fish / translucent marine creatures / floating objects / sea-surface light] as the main subject, but heavily surreal — do not replicate realistically; transform into a striking artistic image. Incorporate: hazy mist, gradient seawater, floating particles, soft focus, light halos, subtle grain, blurred edges, dreamcore atmosphere, low-contrast background, ethereal negative space, floating composition.\n[Composition] Clear focal point; large negative space, off-center, floating layout, poster-style cropping, upper/lower layering, rhythmic density, depth contrast, single-side title, corner info. Like a genuine design poster, not a wallpaper.\n[Color & Atmosphere] Palette around [primary color: coral orange / misty pink / sea-salt blue / deep-sea black / neon purple / gray-green / amber gold]. Unified, soft, airy; subtle film grain, matte, slight print effect. Keywords: serene, ethereal, melancholic, healing, hazy, dreamy, surreal, poetic.\n[Text Layout] Complete ENGLISH typesetting in the image — Main title: [English main title] / Subtitle: [short copy] / fine print [1/2/3]. Restrained sophisticated, no advertising vibe, no clutter. No real brand names, watermarks, garbled text, or dates.\n[Texture] High-end art-poster texture, soft-focus photo feel, dreamy ocean atmosphere, printed grain, modern design. Output: complete finished poster. | All visible text/typography in ENGLISH only.",
      "prompt_ko": "세로 3:4 아트 포스터(완전히 완성·레이아웃). 테마 [테마] — 평범한 바다 사진·물고기 일러스트가 아니라 강한 감성·몽환·분위기의 컨셉추얼 포스터. [핵심] 어류 떼/해파리/열대어/발광어/반투명 해양생물/수면 빛을 주제로 하되 사실 복제 금지, 초현실 변형. 안개·그라데이션 바닷물·부유 입자·소프트포커스·광륜·미세 그레인·흐린 엣지·드림코어·저대비·이서리얼 여백·부유 구성. [구성] 명확한 초점, 넓은 여백·오프센터·포스터 크롭·상하 레이어링·깊이 대비. [색·분위기] [주색](코랄오렌지/미스티핑크/씨솔트블루/딥씨블랙/네온퍼플/그레이그린/앰버골드) 중심, 통일·부드러움·에어리, 필름그레인·매트. 키워드: 고요·이서리얼·멜랑콜릭·힐링·헤이지·드리미·초현실·시적. [텍스트] 완전한 타이포(메인타이틀/부제/카피/파인프린트), 절제·세련, 광고티·잡동사니 금지, 실제 브랜드명·워터마크·오타·날짜 금지. [질감] 하이엔드 아트포스터·소프트포커스·몽환 바다·인쇄 그레인. 출력: 완성 포스터. (원문은 중국어 타이포 명시 → 영어 텍스트로 생성)",
