      "prompt": "2x2 grid, 16:9, do this for 4 confusing days in history: Style = {\n  <pastel_public_service_anime_cinema>\n  MEDIUM: Soft editorial infographic illustration fused with stylized anime-cinematic scene design.\n  SURFACE: Matte paper texture, gentle grain, lightly speckled poster finish, soft digital paint with clean simplified rendering.\n  FORM: Cute stylized characters and readable symbolic objects placed inside a clear poster-like composition.\n  COLOR: Public-service pastel palette with sky blue, medical blue, mint green, blush pink, cream, pale coral, and soft beige, accented by a few darker blue anchors.\n  LIGHTING: Bright soft ambient light overall, with selective dramatic shafts of light and mild cinematic glow around the central subject.\n  COMPOSITION: Clear poster hierarchy with a strong central focal subject, simplified surrounding figures, readable supporting icons, and broad background shapes.\n  MOOD: Hopeful, civic-minded, emotionally uplifting, but with an undercurrent of seriousness and heroic urgency.\n  </pastel_public_service_anime_cinema>\n\n  <transformation>\n  - Convert the subject into a stylized anime-inspired figure or object placed within a clean public-information poster layout.\n  - Reinterpret surrounding elements as simplified symbolic support graphics, civic icons, educational motifs, or narrative support figures.\n  - Convert realism into soft rounded shapes, approachable cartoon proportions, and emotionally readable facial or focal expressions.\n  - Balance gentle infographic clarity with subtle cinematic staging and heroic emphasis.\n  - Rebuild complex environments as simplified scenic backdrops with broad readable forms, soft atmosphere, and reduced clutter.\n  - Convert intense action, tension, or conflict into softened poster drama: readable, emotional, and symbolic rather than gritty or graphic.\n  - Use emblematic objects, badges, shields, charts, globes, or institutional motifs to support the composition when relevant.\n  - Preserve the subject identity, but make it feel like the centerpiece of a noble public-awareness campaign with anime-cinematic charm.\n  </transformation>\n\n  <shape_language>\n  - Favor rounded silhouettes, clean outlines, soft geometry, and approachable figure design.\n  - Keep secondary figures simple and readable.\n  - Use icon-like props, large symbolic forms, and poster-friendly spatial arrangement.\n  - Let emotional storytelling come through pose, spacing, and composition rather than dense detail.\n  </shape_language>\n\n  <rendering_rules>\n  - Keep surfaces soft and matte.\n  - Use subtle paper grain and pastel color blocking.\n  - Avoid hard realism; keep facial and figure design stylized and cute.\n  - Let the composition read clearly from a distance like an educational poster.\n  - Add just enough cinematic atmosphere to create emotional lift.\n  </rendering_rules>\n\n  <finish>\n  - Pastel public-service anime poster aesthetic.\n  - Soft, hopeful, symbolic, and clean.\n  - Educational editorial clarity fused with character-centered cinematic emotion.\n  </finish>\n\n  <avoid>\n  - Avoid gritty gore, realism, or harsh tactical detail.\n  - Avoid dense background clutter.\n  - Avoid overly dark palettes or aggressive contrast.\n  </avoid>\n}",
      "gen_prompt": "A 2x2 grid, 16:9, of four pastel public-service anime-cinematic infographic poster panels, each illustrating a different dramatic moment from history as a hopeful civic-awareness campaign. Soft editorial infographic illustration fused with stylized anime-cinematic scene design; matte paper texture, gentle grain, lightly speckled poster finish, soft digital paint, clean simplified rendering. Cute stylized characters and readable symbolic objects in clear poster-like compositions. Public-service pastel palette: sky blue, medical blue, mint green, blush pink, cream, pale coral, soft beige, accented by a few darker blue anchors. Bright soft ambient light with selective dramatic shafts of light and mild cinematic glow around each central subject. Each panel: clear poster hierarchy, a strong central focal figure, simplified surrounding figures, readable civic icons (badges, shields, charts, globes, institutional motifs), broad background shapes. Rounded silhouettes, clean outlines, soft geometry, approachable cute proportions. Hopeful, civic-minded, emotionally uplifting yet with heroic urgency. Surfaces soft and matte, pastel color blocking, reads clearly from a distance like an educational poster. Avoid gritty realism, gore, dense clutter, dark palettes or harsh contrast.",
      "prompt_ko": "'역사 속 헷갈리는 날들'을 시각화하는 2x2 그리드(16:9) 스타일 템플릿. 스타일=파스텔 공익광고풍 애니-시네마틱 인포그래픽 포스터. 매트 종이 질감·은은한 그레인·반점 포스터 마감·부드러운 디지털 페인트. 귀엽고 양식화된 캐릭터+읽기 쉬운 상징 오브제를 명확한 포스터 구도에. 공익 파스텔 팔레트(스카이블루·메디컬블루·민트·블러시핑크·크림·페일코랄·베이지+소수 다크블루 앵커). 전체적으로 밝고 부드러운 앰비언트+선택적 극적 광선·은은한 시네마틱 글로우. 강한 중심 초점+단순화된 주변 인물+읽기 쉬운 시민 아이콘(배지·방패·차트·지구본·기관 모티프)+넓은 배경 형태. 둥근 실루엣·깔끔한 외곽선·접근하기 쉬운 귀여운 비율. 희망적·시민적·정서적 고양+영웅적 긴박감. 거친 사실주의·고어·산만한 배경·어두운 팔레트 금지.",
