      "prompt": "Heart Foods Prompt\nPrompt: Create a premium viral health infographic poster in minimalist Ayurveda style. Soft beige textured background with subtle botanical doodles. Large bold dark green title “Heart Foods” on top. Centerpiece: a realistic human heart shape made entirely from healthy foods (pomegranate seeds, oats, pistachios, red grapes, beetroot), hyper-detailed food texture, photorealistic, clean studio lighting, top-view composition. Add ingredient labels with sleek rounded tags and short health descriptions. On the right side add a vertical “Benefits” panel with icons like heart health, blood pressure, antioxidants, blood circulation, overall wellness. Clean luxury wellness Instagram aesthetic, high-detail, symmetrical composition, viral infographic style, ultra realistic, premium nutrition poster.\n\nBone Foods Prompt: same template, centerpiece a human bone made from yogurt, kale, black sesame, almonds, figs, amaranth; benefit icons: bone density, stronger bones, joint support, essential nutrients.\n\nSkin Foods Prompt: same template, centerpiece a side-profile face made from almonds, oranges, tomatoes, paneer cubes; benefit icons: glowing skin, hydration, skin repair, anti-aging, overall skin health.\n\nGut Foods Prompt: same template, centerpiece stomach and intestines made from yogurt, coconut, papaya, pear, chia seeds, fennel; benefit icons: healthy gut, digestion support, immunity boost, reduces bloating, regular bowel movement.\n\nLiver Foods Prompt: same template, centerpiece a liver shape made from coriander leaves, garlic cloves, turmeric powder, radish slices, lemon slices; benefit icons: detoxifies liver, supports liver function, improves bile production, antioxidants.",
      "prompt_ko": "Ayurveda 미니멀 스타일 바이럴 헬스 인포그래픽 시리즈. 베이지 텍스처 배경+식물 두들. 굵은 다크그린 타이틀. 센터피스=신체 장기/부위 형태를 그 부위에 좋은 실제 식재료로 형상화(포토리얼, 하이퍼디테일 푸드텍스처, 스튜디오조명, 탑뷰). 재료 라벨(둥근 태그)+짧은 효능 설명. 우측(또는 하단) 세로 Benefits 패널에 아이콘 나열. 럭셔리 웰니스 인스타 미학, 대칭 구도, 바이럴 인포그래픽 스타일. Heart(석류씨·귀리·피스타치오·적포도·비트)/Bone(요거트·케일·흑임자·아몬드·무화과·아마란스)/Skin(아몬드·오렌지·토마토·파니르)/Gut(요거트·코코넛·파파야·배·치아시드·펜넬)/Liver(고수·마늘·강황가루·무·레몬) 5종, 장기모양×식재료×혜택아이콘 3슬롯만 바꾸는 앵커+슬롯 패턴.",
