      "prompt": "Nana banana pro promotional Cinematic prompt\n\nCreate a premium vertical 3:4 cinematic AR poster featuring a young beautiful woman holding a smartphone in her hand as the central subject. She looks stylish, modern, with a natural realistic appearance, expressive eyes, and a confident relaxed pose, as if she is listening to music and choosing tracks. One hand holds the smartphone, the other can interact with floating music interface elements around her. Surround her with a dynamic orbiting system of floating 3D music interface cards, as if she is inside an augmented reality music player environment. The cards should feel like Spotify and Apple Music inspired UI elements, floating around her at different depths. Some cards are in the foreground, partially overlapping the frame, while others drift behind her, creating depth and motion. Each floating interface card must contain one clearly readable rock-style track title. Make the typography sharp, clean, modern, and highly legible. Use these track names exactly, each on its own separate card: Midnight Riot, Electric Bones, Wild Echo, Neon Crash, Broken Anthem, Black Voltage, Storm Signal, Rebel Hearts. Important: the track names must be easy to read, correctly spelled, and visually prominent. Avoid distorted, broken, or unreadable text.\n\nStyle of the interface cards: translucent frosted glass, glassmorphism, soft rounded corners, subtle glowing borders, elegant UI design, realistic reflections, premium futuristic music app aesthetic. Include album cover thumbnails, play buttons, equalizer bars, progress bars, and subtle waveform graphics.\n\nMood and aesthetic: rock-inspired but clean and premium, cinematic, editorial, futuristic, stylish, energetic. The scene should feel like a high-end music campaign or fashion-tech poster.\n\nLighting: professional studio-quality lighting with soft glow from the floating interface cards illuminating her face and hands. Natural skin tones, realistic beauty lighting, slightly dramatic contrast, subtle rim light, polished commercial photo quality.\n\nComposition: medium shot or medium-wide shot, visually balanced but dynamic, with strong depth of field. The woman remains sharply in focus, while some foreground and background interface cards have slight cinematic blur to emphasize movement and depth.\n\nBackground: dark moody gradient or atmospheric studio backdrop with subtle rock-concert energy, soft haze, clean shadows, and modern premium color grading. Add subtle red, charcoal, deep graphite, and muted neon accents to enhance the rock mood without making the composition messy.\n\nUltra-realistic, cinematic, highly detailed, luxury editorial music-tech visual, clean composition, realistic hands, realistic smartphone, readable text, polished UI, 8k quality. Aspect ratio: 3:4 vertical.",
      "prompt_ko": "Nano Banana Pro 프로모 시네마틱 프롬프트. 세로 3:4, 스마트폰을 든 여성이 중심 피사체, 다른 한손은 떠다니는 음악 UI와 상호작용. Spotify/Apple Music풍 글래스모피즘 카드가 서로 다른 깊이로 인물 주위를 궤도처럼 부유. 전경 카드는 프레임을 일부 가리고 배경 카드는 뒤로 물러나 깊이감. 카드마다 록스풍 트랙명 하나씩, 정확한 트랙명 리스트를 verbatim 잠금(Midnight Riot / Electric Bones / Wild Echo / Neon Crash / Broken Anthem / Black Voltage / Storm Signal / Rebel Hearts). 앨범커버/플레이버튼/이퀄라이저/프로그레스바/웨이브폼 포함. 록 무드지만 깨끗하고 프리미엄한 분위기, 시네마틱 라이팅. 전경/배경 카드에 따로 뎁스오브필드 블러 차등으로 궤도(orbit) 깊이감 연출. 레드/차콜/그래파이트/뮤트 네온 악센트 톤.",
