      "prompt": "Gpt image 2 on chatgpt\n\nPrompt:\n\nTransform the uploaded reference photo into an ultra-premium **Paper Identity** portrait while preserving the subject's identity with exceptional facial accuracy. The person must remain instantly recognizable, with the exact facial structure, expression, hairstyle, facial hair, skin proportions, pose, body proportions, clothing, and every defining feature faithfully preserved.\n\nRecreate the entire portrait as if handcrafted by a master paper sculptor using hundreds of individually cut, folded, layered, curled, and assembled pieces of premium matte cardstock. Every visible element—including the face, hair, clothing, hands, accessories, and all objects—must be built entirely from layered paper with realistic thickness, crisp cut edges, subtle paper fibers, folded details, and handcrafted depth. The facial likeness is the highest priority.\n\nUse only a monochromatic palette of paper white, ivory, light gray, charcoal, graphite, and black. No colors, paint, plastic, metal, or CGI. Light the sculpture with soft professional studio lighting that enhances the paper layers and realistic shadows.\n\nReplace the background with a pure solid black backdrop for a premium editorial presentation. Compose the image in a 4:5 vertical ratio, maintaining the original pose. The final result should be ultra-high-resolution, museum-quality, and convincingly resemble a real handcrafted paper sculpture photographed in a professional studio.\n\nDo not add or remove anything from the original image. No text, logos, watermarks, borders, glowing effects, vector art, anime, cartoons, glossy materials, metallic finishes, or any element that breaks the illusion of a handcrafted paper masterpiece.",
      "prompt_ko": "원작은 업로드된 레퍼런스 사진 속 인물의 정확한 얼굴/헤어/포즈/의상을 그대로 유지하면서 전신을 '수백 개의 개별 재단·접힘·레이어드 매트 카드스톡'으로 조각한 것처럼 재현하는 페이스락 워크플로. 모노크롬(페이퍼화이트·아이보리·라이트그레이·차콜·그래파이트·블랙)만 사용, 색/페인트/플라스틱/금속/CGI 금지. 순수 블랙 배경, 4:5 세로, 뮤지엄급 스튜디오 사진처럼. 원본에서 더하거나 빼지 않음(텍스트/로고/워터마크/테두리/글로우/벡터아트/애니메이션풍/광택/메탈릭 금지). 레퍼런스 이미지가 없어 gen_prompt는 가상의 인물로 대체.",
      "gen_prompt": "Create an ultra-premium 'Paper Identity' portrait of a middle-aged man with short cropped hair, a neat beard, wearing a simple crew-neck sweater, in a relaxed three-quarter pose with a calm expression. Recreate the entire portrait as if handcrafted by a master paper sculptor using hundreds of individually cut, folded, layered, curled, and assembled pieces of premium matte cardstock. Every visible element — the face, hair, clothing, hands, and all details — must be built entirely from layered paper with realistic thickness, crisp cut edges, subtle paper fibers, folded details, and handcrafted depth. Use only a monochromatic palette of paper white, ivory, light gray, charcoal, graphite, and black. No colors, paint, plastic, metal, or CGI. Soft professional studio lighting enhancing the paper layers and realistic shadows. Pure solid black backdrop, premium editorial presentation. Compose in a 4:5 vertical ratio. Ultra-high-resolution, museum-quality, convincingly resembling a real handcrafted paper sculpture photographed in a professional studio. No text, logos, watermarks, borders, glowing effects, vector art, anime, cartoons, glossy materials, or metallic finishes.",
