      "title": "진행형 아카이브 — 만화 액션 도시에 포스터 (바리스타 PRESSURE SHOT)",
      "prompt": "漫画行动档案海报，16:9横版——泛黄褶皱的牛皮纸背景；精细的黑墨水漫画插画，采用网点点缀，描绘[职业+任务]正在行动中的瞬间，绝无摆拍；红色作为唯一强调色（泼溅颜料、印章、警示条纹、关键数值）；左上角巨型粗体压印二字标题\"[标题]\"，配以三段式斜杠副标题\"[地点 情境 指令]\"；人物周围密布模块化档案网格——参数表、仪表盘、条形码、档案编号、图标条、警告标签——另附2-4个漫画特写插入面板（眼睛、双手、装备），格式如同数据模块；文件必须呈现进行中状态：半勾选的清单，[已完成项]打勾，[待办项]留空，空白日志字段，状态：[进行中]，可选竖排日语标语条——无全彩，无干净纸张，无完成清单，无镜头摆拍。\n\n--- JSON version ---\n{\n  \"style_rules\": {\n    \"background\": \"aged crumpled cream paper texture, full bleed\",\n    \"hero_illustration\": \"black ink manga linework with screentone shading — character captured MID-TASK (reaching, pulling, adjusting), never posing at camera\",\n    \"accent\": \"red is the ONLY color — paint splashes, stamps, hazard stripes, warning panels, key data values\",\n    \"title\": \"giant distressed black ultra-condensed 2-word title, upper left\",\n    \"subtitle\": \"3-segment slash format: [LOCATION/CASE] / [SITUATION] / [DIRECTIVE]\",\n    \"dossier_grid\": \"dense modular panels surrounding illustration: parameter tables, gauges, tool diagrams, file numbers, barcodes, icon strips, stamps, warning labels\",\n    \"live_state_devices\": \"AT LEAST 3 of: half-checked checklist (some ✓ some ☐), blank log fields (date/time/by empty), STATUS: ACTIVE, progress bar partially filled, speech bubble with present-tense imperatives — the paperwork must read as IN PROGRESS, not archived\",\n    \"manga_insert_panels\": \"2-4 close-up panels in the same frame style as data modules: character's eye, hands, equipment detail — emotion formatted as another instrument readout\",\n    \"optional_jp\": \"vertical Japanese slogan strip (調査記録 / 開花禁止 style)\",\n    \"format\": \"16:9 horizontal\"\n  },\n  \"negative\": \"clean white paper, full color palette, fully-checked/finished checklist, character posing at camera, glossy digital UI, empty sparse margins\",\n  \"variables\": {\n    \"profession_task\": \"[lunar mechanic fixing rover / botanist handling carnivorous specimen / barista pulling espresso / rain-night courier]\",\n    \"title\": \"[2-word title: VACUUM FIX / GROWTH CASE / PRESSURE SHOT / MIDNIGHT RUN]\",\n    \"subtitle\": \"[3-segment: BAY 12 / SEAL BREACH / MANUAL OVERRIDE]\",\n    \"data_content\": \"[domain tables: system status / plant profile / brew parameters / route priority]\",\n    \"checklist_split\": \"[which items ✓ vs ☐ — place the 'now' exactly between them, aligned with the character's gesture]\",\n    \"insert_closeups\": \"[eye / hands / gauge / wheel]\",\n    \"status_word\": \"[ACTIVE / SEALED / COMPLETE / HIGH]\"\n  }\n}",
      "prompt_ko": "만화 행동 아카이브 포스터 템플릿(16:9). 핵심 발상 = 진행형 문서(蔡格尼克 효과): 절반만 체크된 체크리스트·빈 로그 필드·STATUS: ACTIVE·반쯤 찬 진행바로 '지금 진행 중' 순간을 포착 — 관객이 미완성을 머릿속에서 완성하게 만듦. 구겨진 미색 종이 + 흑잉크 망가 선화(스크린톤) + 레드 단일 강조색 + 좌상단 대형 2단어 타이틀 + 슬래시 3단 부제 + 모듈러 도시에 그리드(파라미터표/게이지/바코드/파일번호) + 만화 클로즈업 2~4패널 + 세로 일본어 슬로건. 경중 무관 동일 문서규격(에스프레소도 선외수리 임무처럼) = 소년만화 문법의 편집시스템화.",
      "gen_prompt": "Manga action dossier poster, 16:9 horizontal, on aged crumpled cream paper texture, full bleed. Fine black ink manga linework with screentone shading depicting a barista captured mid-task pulling an espresso shot — one hand locking the portafilter, the other reaching for the lever, never posing at camera. Red is the ONLY accent color: paint splashes, rubber stamps, hazard stripes, key data values. Giant distressed black ultra-condensed 2-word title “PRESSURE SHOT” in the upper left, with a 3-segment slash subtitle “BAR 09 / CREMA WINDOW / PULL NOW”. Dense modular dossier grid surrounding the figure: brew parameter table (DOSE 18G, YIELD 36G, TIME 27S, TEMP 93C, PRESSURE 9 BAR), round pressure gauges, barcode, file number, icon strip, red warning label. The paperwork must read as IN PROGRESS: a half-checked checklist with GRIND, DOSE, TAMP ticked and PULL, STEAM, SERVE left empty, blank log fields (DATE/TIME/BY empty), STATUS: ACTIVE, a progress bar two-thirds filled, a small speech bubble with a present-tense imperative “HOLD 9 BAR”. Include 3 manga close-up insert panels formatted like data modules: the barista’s focused eye, hands on the portafilter, the pressure gauge needle. A vertical Japanese slogan strip reading 抽出中. No full color, no clean paper, no finished checklist, no posed shot, no glossy digital UI.",
