      "prompt": "class CulinaryDeconstructionCard_Poster:\n    def __init__(self):\n        self.movements = \"Editorial food photography, mid-century recipe card design, Isotype pictograms\"\n        self. systems = \"Clean deconstructed flat-lay, warm muted palette, generous negative space, tidy grid\"\n        self.material_canvas = \"The poster background is a warm linen and butcher-paper surface with a subtle letterpress texture\"\n        self. data_layer = \"Ingredient callout lines pointing to each component, a radial flavor-note wheel, numbered process-flow arrows, small Isotype pictogram icons, an origin sidebar block\"\n        self.optics = \"overhead flat-lay food photography, soft natural window light, appetizing true color, shallow depth, physically accurate textures\"\n        self.params = \" \" \n    def generate_prompt(self):\n        subject = \"[SUBJECT, e.g., A photorealistic deconstructed gourmet burger]\"\n        return f\"{subject}, {self.optics}, crisp focus, edible unmodified physical object::5 \" \\\n               f\"Graphic Design Poster blending {self.movements}::2.5 \" \\\n               f\"Visual systems applied to the layout: {self. systems}::2 \" \\\n               f\"Informational layer: {self. data_layer}::2.5 \" \\\n               f\"Canvas Material: {self.material_canvas}::2 \" \\\n               f\"unappetizing dull food, cluttered messy layout, subject flattened into illustration, garish colors::-1 {self.params}\"",
      "prompt_ko": "Python 클래스 형식 함수형 템플릿. [SUBJECT] 요리를 해체 플랫레이로 — 에디토리얼 푸드 포토 + 미드센추리 레시피 카드 + Isotype 픽토그램 융합. 재료 콜아웃 라인, 방사형 풍미 휠, 번호 프로세스 화살표, 원산지 사이드바. 리넨+정육지 캔버스, 오버헤드 자연광, 따뜻한 뮤트 팔레트, MJ식 ::N 가중치 구조(재현 시 제거).",
      "gen_prompt": "A photorealistic deconstructed bibimbap, overhead flat-lay food photography, soft natural window light, appetizing true color, shallow depth of field, physically accurate textures, crisp focus, edible unmodified ingredients laid out separately — steamed rice mound, sautéed spinach, julienned carrots, shiitake mushrooms, bean sprouts, zucchini, a raw egg yolk in half shell, gochujang paste in a small dish, sesame seeds and oil. Graphic design poster blending editorial food photography, mid-century recipe card design and Isotype pictograms. Layout systems: clean deconstructed flat-lay, warm muted palette, generous negative space, tidy grid. Informational layer: thin ingredient callout lines pointing to each component with small labels, a radial flavor-note wheel, numbered process-flow arrows showing mixing order, small Isotype pictogram icons, an origin sidebar block reading KOREA · JEONJU. Canvas: warm linen and butcher-paper surface with a subtle letterpress texture. Title “BIBIMBAP” in clean mid-century typography. No dull unappetizing food, no cluttered messy layout, no illustration-flattened subject, no garish colors.",
