      "prompt": "2x2 grid, do this for 4 less known hidden asian manga: class comicdiorama: def __init__(self, franchise, era, sfx, bg): self.franchise = franchise # \"[franchise]\" self.era = era # \"[year]\" self.sfx = sfx # \"[onomatopoeia]\" self. bg = bg # \"[bg_color_descriptor]\" self.scale = \"miniature_action_figure_fidelity\" self.base = \"open_vintage_comic_book_spread\" def base_platform(self): cover = f\"[{self.franchise}] cover art visible at front edge\" pages = \"yellowed spread, original printed panels showing beneath scene\" bridge = \"3d figures erupt upward — page surface is the dimensional floor\" return [cover, pages, bridge] def populate(self): hero = \"[hero] — sculpted 3d figure, era-accurate costume, action pose\" villain = \"[villain] — era-accurate, facing hero in shared 3d space\" env = \"[env_prop] — physical miniature construction rising from page\" return [hero, villain, env] def sfx_layer(self): return { \"text\": self.sfx, \"style\": \"3d extruded bold comic font\", \"material\": \"high-gloss colored resin\", \"shadow\": \"hard cast on page below\", \"tilt\": \"[angle]deg — dynamic, not static\" } def badge(self): return f\"yellow_rect | '{self.franchise.upper()} | {self.era}' | black condensed\" panels = [ comicdiorama(\"[franchise_1]\",\"[era_1]\",\"[sfx_1]\",\"[bg_1]\"), comicdiorama(\"[franchise_2]\",\"[era_2]\",\"[sfx_2]\",\"[bg_2]\"), comicdiorama(\"[franchise_3]\",\"[era_3]\",\"[sfx_3]\",\"[bg_3]\"), comicdiorama(\"[franchise_4]\",\"[era_4]\",\"[sfx_4]\",\"[bg_4]\"), ] render_grid( panels = panels, layout = \"2x2_quad\", medium = \"3d_photorealistic_diorama_miniature\", lens = \"45deg_overhead_isometric\", light = \"studio_softbox + era_color_accent_per_panel\" )",
      "prompt_ko": "Python class 함수형 템플릿(comicdiorama). 구조 = 펼쳐진 빈티지 만화책(표지 앞단 노출+누렇게 바랜 원작 패널 지면)이 차원의 바닥이 되고, 그 위로 히어로·빌런 3D 미니어처 피규어(시대고증 코스튬·액션 포즈)와 환경 소품이 솟아오름. SFX 의성어 = 3D 압출 코믹 폰트·유광 컬러 레진·지면에 하드 섀도우·동적 기울기. 옐로 사각 뱃지(프랜차이즈|연도). 4개 프랜차이즈 변수로 2x2 그리드, 45도 오버헤드 아이소메트릭, 스튜디오 소프트박스+패널별 시대 강조색. 원문 지시=잘 안 알려진 아시아 만화 4종.",
      "gen_prompt": "2x2 grid, four equal square panels, each a photorealistic 3D diorama miniature rising from an open vintage comic book spread, shot from a 45-degree overhead isometric angle with studio softbox lighting and a different era color accent per panel. In every panel: the comic cover art is visible at the front edge, the yellowed spread with original printed manga panels shows beneath the scene, and sculpted miniature action figures erupt upward as if the page surface were the dimensional floor — one hero and one villain in era-accurate costumes facing each other in shared 3D space, plus one physical environment prop rising from the page. Each panel has a big 3D-extruded bold comic onomatopoeia in high-gloss colored resin casting a hard shadow on the page, tilted dynamically, and a small yellow rectangle badge with black condensed text. Panel 1: a 1960s black-and-white ronin manga world, wandering swordsman hero vs masked demon, pagoda prop, resin SFX “ZAN!”, badge “RONIN TALES | 1967”, sepia-ink accent. Panel 2: a 1970s devil-hunter manga, horned antihero vs winged demon, cracked city rooftop prop, resin SFX “GWOOM!”, badge “DARK OATH | 1972”, crimson accent. Panel 3: a 1990s gothic gunslinger manhwa, coat-clad priest hero vs undead baron, ruined chapel prop, resin SFX “BLAM!”, badge “HOLY BULLET | 1998”, ash-violet accent. Panel 4: a late-90s megastructure cyber manga, silent wanderer with graviton rifle vs silicon creature, endless steel corridor prop, resin SFX “KRRRT!”, badge “STEEL ABYSS | 1997”, teal-steel accent. Miniature action-figure fidelity, physically believable materials, clean grid alignment, no real logos, no watermark.",
