      "prompt": "Upload only the official brand logo. Automatically identify the brand and preserve its original logo, typography, colors, proportions, and identity never redesign it.\n\nCreate a hyper-realistic,  ultra-massive 4D logo monument as the world's largest outdoor landmark, occupying most of the frame. Place it in a bright luxury plaza with blue sky, premium landscaping, and an extreme low-angle 24mm IMAX cinematic view. Use Cinema 4D + V-Ray quality with realistic metal, glass, chrome, acrylic, and premium reflections. Add realistic people (tourists, families, employees, photographers, cyclists, security, visitors) to emphasize the enormous scale.\n\nBehind the logo, include the brand's authentic headquarters/factory/campus with modern architecture, loading docks, trucks, and branding. Integrate a clean white Apple-style Swiss design panel at the bottom displaying the official logo, color palette, typography, icon, visual language, packaging style, logo safe area, and brand guidelines.\n\n8K Ultra HD, photorealistic, HDR, Unreal Engine 5 environment, luxury FMCG advertising, IMAX cinematic, perfect lighting, reflections, shadows, and zero noise.",
      "prompt_ko": "공식 브랜드 로고만 업로드하면 → 로고를 세계 최대 야외 랜드마크급 4D 모뉴먼트로: 럭셔리 플라자 + 24mm IMAX 로우앵글, C4D+V-Ray급 금속·유리·크롬 질감, 스케일 강조용 실사 인파, 배경에 브랜드 본사/캠퍼스, 하단에 Apple풍 스위스 디자인 브랜드 가이드라인 패널(로고·팔레트·타이포·세이프에어리어). 로고 아이덴티티 보존이 핵심 규칙.",
      "gen_prompt": "A hyper-realistic, ultra-massive 4D logo monument of the brand wordmark “RIDEUS” as the world largest outdoor landmark, occupying most of the frame. The RIDEUS letters are built in brushed metal and glossy red-accented chrome with glass edges, modern geometric sans-serif, premium and precise. Placed in a bright luxury plaza with blue sky, premium landscaping, and an extreme low-angle 24mm IMAX cinematic view. Cinema 4D + V-Ray quality with realistic metal, glass, chrome, acrylic, and premium reflections. Realistic people around it — tourists, families, employees, photographers, cyclists, security — emphasizing the enormous scale. Behind the monument, the brand headquarters campus with modern architecture, a fleet of premium shuttle buses at loading docks, and rooftop branding. At the bottom, a clean white Apple-style Swiss design panel displaying the RIDEUS logo, a red-black-white color palette, typography specimen, icon, visual language and logo safe area grid, like an official brand guideline sheet. 8K Ultra HD, photorealistic, HDR, luxury advertising, IMAX cinematic, perfect lighting and reflections, zero noise.",
