      "prompt": "Create an ultra-premium advertising poster for Guerlain perfume, in the visual spirit of the Aqua Allegoria line, using a minimalist ingredient-board composition on a clean pale ivory-warm-gray background. The image should feel fresh, refined, precise, airy, and extremely luxurious, like an international fragrance campaign with highly controlled composition and couture-level still-life photography.\n\nMain composition:\nPlace one realistic Guerlain Aqua Allegoria perfume bottle exactly at the center as the absolute hero object. The bottle must be unmistakably Guerlain: elegant transparent glass bottle, luminous pale golden perfume liquid, refined honeycomb texture, iconic rounded gold cap, crisp luxurious label, crystal-clear reflections, and exquisite premium detail. The bottle should be the brightest, clearest, and most luminous object in the image.\n\nComposition structure:\nArrange the fragrance-note ingredients in a restrained, spread-out, flat-lay-inspired composition around the bottle, not as a wreath, not as a bouquet, and not as a dense decorative frame. The note elements should feel gently laid out on the same surface behind and around the bottle, with open spacing, calm visual balance, and strong editorial restraint. The bottle remains dominant while the ingredients act as a refined composition board.\n\nFragrance-note layout:\nCreate four carefully art-directed note clusters around the central Guerlain bottle:\ntop left: fresh mandarin and bergamot slices, glossy citrus peel, a few dew droplets\ntop right: delicate white floral cluster such as orange blossom and neroli petals, with elegant green leaves\nbottom left: a fresh basil or green aromatic herb cluster, clean, sculptural, vibrant, premium\nbottom right: soft white musk-inspired element interpreted as smooth pale material, translucent petals, or clean airy white botanical texture, with a few crystal-clear droplets\n\nVisual language:\nThe surrounding ingredients should be slightly deeper, richer, and more saturated than the perfume bottle itself, so the transparent bottle stands out clearly. The ingredient clusters must feel premium, hyper-real, fresh, tactile, and materially rich, like botanical specimens in a luxury fragrance editorial. Keep them restrained, crisp, and sculptural, never messy.\n\nBackground:\nUse a very clean pale ivory-gray or warm light stone background with no environmental clutter. The surface should feel softly matte, smooth, and expensive. Add only subtle natural shadows beneath each element to create depth while preserving the flat, controlled, and elevated luxury-ad look.\n\nTypography:\nTypography must be extremely minimal, elegant, and editorial. Do not place any scattered small black text in the upper-left corner. Keep the layout elevated and quiet. Place a clean centered title at the top:\n“GUERLAIN”\n“AQUA ALLEGORIA”\n\nUnder the bottle, place a restrained supporting line:\n“mandarin, bergamot, neroli, basil, white musk”\nor\n“fresh clarity in botanical couture”\n\nOptional refined Chinese support in very small tasteful typography:\n“娇兰香水”\n“极简清爽”\n“精致到每一寸细节”\n\nAdd tiny elegant labels near the ingredient clusters if needed:\n“MANDARIN”\n“NEROLI”\n“BASIL”\n“WHITE MUSK”\nor bilingual minimalist labels:\n“柑橘”\n“橙花”\n“罗勒”\n“白麝香”\n\nThe labels should be very subtle, airy, and integrated into the composition.\n\nColor palette:\npale ivory background,\ntransparent golden perfume tone,\nfresh citrus yellow,\nleaf green,\nsoft white petals,\nwarm gold accents,\nclear dew highlights.\nThe overall palette should feel clean, refreshing, luminous, and expensive.\n\nMood:\nclean, fresh, luminous, precise, restrained, botanical, couture, luxurious, airy, highly detailed, editorial, calm, elegant, unforgettable.\n\nRendering:\nhyper-detailed luxury perfume photography, pristine glass reflections, realistic citrus texture, crisp leaf detail, delicate white petals, subtle water droplets, elegant soft shadows, 8k, international fragrance campaign quality, minimal but powerful, extremely refined.\n\nNegative prompt:\ncrowded composition, wreath arrangement, bouquet styling, messy props, dark dramatic background, weak Guerlain identity, blurry bottle, cheap cosmetic ad, too much text, upper-left scattered black text, plain black font, low detail, random filler objects, overdecorated scene, childish layout",
      "prompt_ko": "겔랑 아쿠아 알레고리아 무드의 성분 보드 포스터. 정중앙 히어로 보틀(투명 유리·페일골드 액체·허니콤 텍스처·골드 캡)이 화면에서 가장 밝고 선명한 오브젝트. 주변에 향 노트 성분들을 화환/부케/프레임이 아닌 **절제된 플랫레이식 산개 배치** — 같은 평면에 살짝 놓인 듯한 개방 간격. 아이보리-웜그레이 배경, 꾸뛰르급 정물 사진 무드.",
