      "title": "동사 조각 — 단어가 뜻을 연기하는 클라우드 설치물 ([단어] → RIDE)",
      "prompt": "云端未来建筑海报，16:9 横版——画面上方悬浮着一整座由白色参数化编织网格结构搭建的巨型英文单词雕塑「[单词]」，镂空篮编质感，字母彼此融合成连续的雕塑体，整体姿态直接表演这个词的动作：[姿态描述]；雕塑底部垂下细缆绳，像根系一样向下吊住一块悬浮在云层之上的浅蓝白色平台，平台带玻璃栏杆和一块珊瑚粉圆形地面区，建成与词义对应的完整设施：[设施内容]，画面中有真人和一两个机器人在使用这座设施；天空湛蓝，云层洁白浓密，云层之下隐约露出远处城市天际线；平台边缘左下角有一条英文标签条\"[标签文字]\"配一枚[图标]；整体明亮日光、建筑效果图级质感，画面所有文字均为英文——不要出现除主词以外的其他文字、不要密集难读的文字块、不要暗色夜景、不要地面视角的城市街景、不要字母之间材质不统一、不要文字只是平躺无姿态的普通字体\n\n--- JSON version ---\n{\n  \"style_rules\": {\n    \"typography_sculpture\": \"one giant monumental 3D letterform sculpture of a single English word, built entirely from white woven parametric lattice/mesh structure (basket-weave architectural texture), letters merge into one continuous sculptural form, floating above the clouds\",\n    \"semantic_pose\": \"the sculpture's overall silhouette performs the word's own meaning/action rather than just standing upright as flat letters\",\n    \"suspension\": \"thin cables run from the base of the lettering down to a floating platform below, like roots anchoring the sculpture\",\n    \"sky_setting\": \"bright blue sky, dense white cloud layer beneath the sculpture and platform, a hazy distant city skyline visible at the horizon under the clouds\",\n    \"platform_facility\": \"sleek light blue-white floating platform with glass railings and one coral-pink circular floor zone, built out as a complete facility matching the word's meaning, populated with small human figures (plus one or two robots) actively using it\",\n    \"signage\": \"small English label bar in the bottom-left corner of the platform edge, format '[theme] / [subtitle]' with one matching line-icon\",\n    \"rendering\": \"bright clean daylight, architectural-visualization quality lighting\",\n    \"format\": \"16:9 horizontal\"\n  },\n  \"negative\": \"any word/letters other than the one sculpted word, dense unreadable text blocks, dark or night lighting, ground-level city viewpoint, mismatched lattice textures between letters, letters standing as flat generic typography with no pose\",\n  \"variables\": {\n    \"word\": \"[READ / BLOOM / SOUND / ORBIT]\",\n    \"pose_shape\": \"[pages unfurling outward / petals blooming outward / ribbon rippling into a wave knot / ring encircling with orbiting spheres]\",\n    \"facility\": \"[cloud library with bookshelves and reading nooks / sky garden with planting beds and greenhouses / air stage with instruments and speakers / cloud observatory with telescopes and star charts]\",\n    \"label_text\": \"[cloud library / open hours / sky garden / fresh picks / air stage / session one / cloud observatory / night preview]\",\n    \"icon\": \"[book icon / plant icon / logo icon / orbit icon]\"\n  }\n}",
      "prompt_ko": "거대 영단어 조각(화이트 파라메트릭 위빙 격자)이 구름 위에 떠 있는데, **조형 자체가 그 단어의 동작을 연기**(BLOOM=꽃잎처럼 펼쳐짐, SOUND=음파 매듭, ORBIT=고리에 감김). 글자 밑 케이블이 뿌리처럼 내려와 **단어 뜻에 대응하는 클라우드 시설**(READ=도서관, BLOOM=정원)이 있는 부유 플랫폼(라이트블루+코랄핑크 원형 존, 유리 난간)을 매닮. 사람+로봇 이용중, 구름 아래 도시 스카이라인, 건축 렌더급 조명. 中템플릿+JSON. '고정구조×가변요소'의 동사조각 편.",
      "gen_prompt": "A futuristic cloud-architecture poster, 16:9 horizontal. Floating above a dense white cloud layer, one giant monumental 3D letterform sculpture of the English word “RIDE”, built entirely from white woven parametric lattice basket-weave structure, letters merging into one continuous sculptural form — and the sculpture’s whole silhouette performs the word’s meaning: the letters lean forward in a dynamic surging motion, the R stretched like a rider leaning into speed, the E trailing streamlined ribbons like motion lines. Thin cables run from the base of the lettering down like roots, suspending a sleek light blue-white floating platform with glass railings and one coral-pink circular floor zone, built as a miniature shuttle terminal: two small white-and-red shuttle buses at charging docks, a waiting lounge with canopy, tiny real people and one or two robots boarding. Bright blue sky, thick clean clouds beneath, a hazy distant city skyline at the horizon under the clouds. At the platform’s lower-left edge, an English label strip reading “RIDE — CLOUD TERMINAL 01” with a small bus icon. Bright daylight, architectural visualization quality. No other text besides the main word and label, no dark night scene, no ground-level street view, consistent lattice material across all letters.",
