      "prompt": "2x2 grid, 16:9, do this for 4 scifi movies:  \n  environment:\n    background: \"Warm beige hex # F5F5DC\"\n    perspective: \"Isometric 3/4 View\"\n    \n  diorama_base_layer:\n    theme: \"AI_INFER(Primary setting from [FRANCHISE/IP])\"\n    contents: \"AI_INFER(Characters interacting with era-accurate furniture)\"\n    cutaway: true # Front walls removed\n    \n  diorama_upper_layer:\n    theme: \"AI_INFER(Secondary setting from [FRANCHISE/IP])\"\n    contents: \"AI_INFER(Characters interacting with lore-specific props)\"\n    cutaway: true\n    depends_on:\n      - diorama_base_layer\n      \n  scattered_artifacts:\n    placement: \"Resting on the environment background, outside the diorama\"\n    items: \n      - \"AI_INFER(Iconic item 1 from [FRANCHISE/IP])\"\n      - \"AI_INFER(Iconic item 2 from [FRANCHISE/IP])\"\n\n# OUTPUT CONSTRAINT: Render as a highly polished, tactile 3D designer toy set.",
      "prompt_ko": "YAML 구조 템플릿. [프랜차이즈]의 1차 무대(하층)+2차 무대(상층)를 컷어웨이 2층 디오라마로 쌓고, 주변 배경엔 상징 아이템들을 흩어놓는 구성. 웜베이지 배경, 아이소메트릭 3/4 뷰, '광택 나는 촉감형 3D 디자이너 토이셋' 출력 제약이 핵심. 원문=SF영화 4편 2x2.",
      "gen_prompt": "A 2x2 grid, 16:9, four highly polished tactile 3D designer toy diorama sets on a warm beige #F5F5DC background, isometric 3/4 view, each a two-layer cutaway diorama with front walls removed and iconic items scattered on the background outside the diorama. Panel 1 KOREAN POJANGMACHA: lower layer an orange-tent street food stall with a vendor grilling skewers and two stools of customers, upper layer a tiny kitchen prep loft; scattered soju bottle and fish-cake skewer. Panel 2 PC BANG: lower layer rows of glowing gaming desks with two players mid-match, upper layer a snack counter with instant noodle steam; scattered headset and cup-noodle. Panel 3 NORAEBANG: lower layer a neon karaoke room with a singer mid-note and tambourine friend, upper layer the hallway desk with songbooks; scattered microphone and disco ball. Panel 4 HANOK GUESTHOUSE: lower layer a wooden courtyard with guests having tea, upper layer a tiled-roof loft bedroom with folded bedding; scattered brass kettle and hanbok slippers. Miniature toy-like proportions, glossy tactile materials, soft studio light, consistent collectible toy-set finish, thin gutters between panels.",
