      "prompt": "{\n  \"style_rules\": {\n    \"paper_texture\": \"aged cream dossier paper background, palette limited to black, deep blue and white only\",\n    \"dual_portrait\": \"the SAME character drawn twice in one frame — a large calm half-body portrait gazing off to the side (identity shot), overlapping a smaller full-body dynamic action pose of the same character actively doing the job\",\n    \"aura_effect\": \"the action pose is wrapped in an unnatural electric-blue swirl/vortex effect standing in for whatever physical force is present (water splash, wind, dust/impact, smoke/flame) — always rendered the same blue regardless of real-world material, like a shonen-manga power aura\",\n    \"backdrop_diagram\": \"technical blueprint-style line-art specific to the profession filling the background behind the portrait\",\n    \"title_block\": \"bold 2-word stacked title (top word black, bottom word blue), followed by a 3-part slash subtitle (role code / event code / status code)\",\n    \"info_panels\": \"surrounding profile box + equipment/spec list + small photo-inset thumbnails + one badge/flag icon\",\n    \"footer\": \"dossier number + barcode + clearance/status tag at bottom\",\n    \"format\": \"16:9 horizontal\"\n  },\n  \"negative\": \"realistic fire/water/dust colors on the aura effect, single-scale character with no dual portrait, colors beyond cream/black/blue/white, clean non-technical background, missing dossier number or barcode\",\n  \"variables\": {\n    \"profession\": \"[night bike courier / high-altitude weather pilot / desert rally mechanic / artisan tea roaster]\",\n    \"title\": \"[NIGHT COURIER / SKY VECTOR / DUST CREW / FIRE LEAF]\",\n    \"subtitle_3part\": \"[DISTRICT RUN / ROUTE 07 / SIGNAL CLEAR · UPPER AIR / PRESSURE WATCH / UNIT 12 · SERVICE BAY / STAGE 03 / TORQUE READY · SMALL BATCH / SPRING HARVEST / BATCH 24]\",\n    \"backdrop_diagram_type\": \"[subway route map / barometric pressure chart / rally stage route card / tea plant botanical diagram]\",\n    \"info_content\": \"[route photo+wheel detail+clearance level / flight helmet+pressure gauge+atmospheric chart / tire tread+service flag+warning tag / tea packets+origin map+mountain workshop]\"\n  }\n}",
      "prompt_ko": "같은 캐릭터를 한 프레임에 두 번(정면 반신 아이덴티티 샷 + 액션 포즈) 그리는 도시에(dossier) 템플릿. 액션 포즈는 소재 불문 항상 동일한 일렉트릭 블루 소용돌이 오라로 감싸고, 배경엔 직업별 청사진 다이어그램. 크림·블랙·블루·화이트 4색 제한, 2단 타이틀+3단 서브타이틀+스펙패널+도시에 번호/바코드. 직업/타이틀/서브타이틀/배경다이어그램/정보내용 가변.",
      "gen_prompt": "Retro dossier-style editorial illustration on aged cream dossier paper, palette limited to black, deep blue and white only. The same character — a night bike courier — drawn twice in one frame: a large calm half-body portrait gazing off to the side as an identity shot, overlapping a smaller full-body dynamic action pose of the same courier actively riding through the night. The action pose is wrapped in an unnatural electric-blue swirl/vortex aura effect standing in for wind and speed, like a shonen-manga power aura. A technical blueprint-style subway route map fills the background behind the portrait. Bold 2-word stacked title \"NIGHT COURIER\" (top word black, bottom word blue), followed by a 3-part slash subtitle \"DISTRICT RUN / ROUTE 07 / SIGNAL CLEAR\". Surrounding profile box with equipment/spec list, small route photo and wheel-detail thumbnails, and a clearance-level badge/flag icon. Footer with dossier number, barcode, and clearance/status tag. 16:9 horizontal format.",
