      "prompt": "2x2 grid, 16:9, do this for 4 unusual looking car concepts that were real: class GrandExpositionDossier_Poster:\n    def __init__(self):\n        self.movements = \"Belle Epoque exposition plates, Beaux-Arts ornament, Art Nouveau engraving\"\n        self.palette = \"dominant deep burgundy and ivory, secondary antique gold, single jewel-emerald accent, aged warm varnish over all\"\n        self.composition = \"a central hero medallion framed by symmetrical satellite vignettes, an ornate engraved border, a ribbon banner header, and a decorative spec cartouche lower-center\"\n        self.systems = \"dense symmetrical broadsheet layout, fine engraved linework, ornamental rule dividers\"\n        self.data_layer = \"framed detail vignettes of the subject's features, engraved medallion callouts, a scrolled specification cartouche, an ornamental timeline ribbon, small numbered figure references\"\n        self.material_canvas = \"richly aged cream broadsheet paper with a subtle letterpress bite and a gilt-edged border\"\n        self.optics = \"photoreal hero centerpiece integrated into the engraved surround, warm museum lighting, physically accurate premium materials, fine focus\"\n        self.params = \"--stylize 250 --chaos 8 --sref [HERITAGE_CODE] --sw 200 --ar 4:5\"\n    def generate_prompt(self):\n        subject = \"[SUBJECT, e.g., A photorealistic gold skeleton pocket watch]\"\n        return f\"{subject}, {self.optics}, crisp focus, unmodified physical object::5 \" \\\n               f\"Graphic Design Poster blending {self.movements}::2.5 \" \\\n               f\"Compositional structure: {self.composition}::3 \" \\\n               f\"Design system: {self.systems}; color architecture: {self.palette}::2 \" \\\n               f\"Informational layer: {self.data_layer}::2.5 \" \\\n               f\"Canvas Material: {self.material_canvas}::2 \" \\\n               f\"flat sparse layout, modern minimal design, subject rendered as line engraving, cheap plastic object, cluttered unreadable mess::-1 {self.params}\"",
      "prompt_ko": "벨에포크 박람회 판화×보자르 장식×아르누보 엔그레이빙을 결합한 골동품풍 스펙 포스터 클래스. 버건디+아이보리+골드+에메랄드 팔레트, 중앙 메달리온+대칭 위성 비네트+장식 테두리+리본 배너+스펙 카투슈. 원본 트윗은 클래식/컨셉카 4종 2x2 그리드용, subject만 바꾸면 임의 오브제(시계·카메라 등)에도 적용 가능한 범용 골동품 도시에 템플릿.",
      "gen_prompt": "A photorealistic gold skeleton pocket watch as the crisp-focus, unmodified physical hero centerpiece, integrated into an engraved surround with warm museum lighting and physically accurate premium materials, fine focus. Graphic design poster blending Belle Epoque exposition plates, Beaux-Arts ornament, and Art Nouveau engraving. Compositional structure: a central hero medallion framed by symmetrical satellite vignettes, an ornate engraved border, a ribbon banner header, and a decorative spec cartouche lower-center. Design system: dense symmetrical broadsheet layout, fine engraved linework, ornamental rule dividers; color architecture: dominant deep burgundy and ivory, secondary antique gold, single jewel-emerald accent, aged warm varnish over all. Informational layer: framed detail vignettes of the watch's features, engraved medallion callouts, a scrolled specification cartouche, an ornamental timeline ribbon, small numbered figure references. Canvas material: richly aged cream broadsheet paper with a subtle letterpress bite and a gilt-edged border. 4:5 aspect ratio. No flat sparse layout, no modern minimal design, no line-engraving-only rendering, no cheap plastic look, no cluttered unreadable mess.",
