      "prompt": "class Fashion_Habitat_Poster_DNA:\n    def __init__(self):\n        self.subject = \"[GARMENT / SNEAKER / BAG / JEWELRY / FASHION COLLECTION]\"\n\n        self.parent_styles = {\n            \"composition\": \"Luxury fashion campaign with sculptural garment presentation\",\n            \"rendering\": \"Ultra-premium exploded-view product advertisement showing materials and construction\",\n            \"graphic_system\": \"Avant-garde runway invitation typography with editorial spacing\",\n            \"detail_language\": \"Architectural section drawing and textile craft diagram\"\n        }\n\n        self.mutations = {\n            \"semantic_mutation\": \"The garment becomes a wearable building, shelter, or ecosystem\",\n            \"scale_mutation\": \"Fibers become roads, seams become bridges, folds become landscapes\",\n            \"information_mutation\": \"Callouts identify fabric, stitching, silhouette, movement, origin, and cultural references\",\n            \"medium_mutation\": \"Glossy editorial photography mixed with pattern-cutting blueprint lines\"\n        }\n\n    def generate_subject(self):\n        subject = \"\"\"\n        Create a vertical poster for [FASHION SUBJECT].\n        Present the garment or accessory as a floating hero object, partially exploded into panels,\n        seams, fasteners, textile layers, hardware, lining, silhouette guides, and motion paths.\n\n        Transform the piece into a miniature architectural habitat.\n        Show how its materials, folds, and construction create a world of shelter, identity,\n        performance, and cultural meaning.\n        \"\"\"\n        return render(\n            subject,\n            format=\"vertical luxury fashion poster\",\n            typography=\"[COLLECTION NAME] / [GARMENT TYPE] / [ATELIER CODE]\",\n            output_rules=\"premium fabric detail, controlled exploded layout, elegant negative space, editorial typography\",\n            negative_prompt=\"no cheap catalog look, no random model pose, no clutter, no watermark\"\n        )",
      "prompt_ko": "의류/액세서리를 '입을 수 있는 건축물·생태계'로 변환하는 익스플로디드뷰 패션 포스터 DNA. 원단 섬유는 도로, 봉제선은 다리, 주름은 지형이 되는 '스케일 뮤테이션'이 핵심. 럭셔리 캠페인 구도+제품 익스플로디드뷰 렌더링+런웨이 초청장 타이포+건축 단면도 디테일 언어의 조합. [GARMENT]/[COLLECTION NAME]/[ATELIER CODE] 가변.",
      "gen_prompt": "Vertical luxury fashion poster for an oversized cream wool trench coat, presented as a floating hero object, partially exploded into panels, seams, fasteners, textile layers, hardware, lining, silhouette guides, and motion paths. The coat is transformed into a miniature architectural habitat — its wool fibers become roads, its seams become bridges, its folds become rolling landscapes — showing how its materials and construction create a world of shelter, identity, performance, and cultural meaning. Luxury fashion campaign with sculptural garment presentation, ultra-premium exploded-view product advertisement showing materials and construction, avant-garde runway invitation typography with editorial spacing, architectural section drawing and textile craft diagram detail language. Typography reads \"WINTER HABITAT / TRENCH COAT / ATELIER NO.09\". Premium fabric detail, controlled exploded layout, elegant negative space, editorial typography. No cheap catalog look, no random model pose, no clutter, no watermark.",
