      "prompt": "GPT Prompt -> input_topic ::= \"<insert movie / game / manga / franchise here>\"\n\n[topic_analysis] — translate input_topic into a design studio:\n\n* hero form: the franchise's signature vehicle or object as a full-scale industrial styling-clay development model.\n* surface state: matte styling clay on one half, di-noc film on the other half to preview the finish.\n* tape drawing: masking-tape section lines on the model and a profile tape-drawing on the studio wall behind.\n* reflection read: striped black-and-white reflection boards or ceiling light lines reading across the surface to show highlights.\n* studio floor: a turntable, a tool board with clay rakes and slicks, and a nearby scale buck.\n\n<scene> ::= <studio_floor> \"+\" <hero_clay> \"+\" <dinoc_half> \"+\" <tape_drawing> \"+\" <reflection_read> \"+\" <repro>\n\n<studio_floor> ::= \"a design-studio floor with a turntable and a tool board of clay rakes and slicks\"\n<hero_clay> ::= \"the hero form as a full-scale matte styling-clay model, taped section lines across its surfaces\"\n<dinoc_half> ::= \"di-noc film wrapping one half to preview the finished paint and glazing\"\n<tape_drawing> ::= \"a full-size profile tape drawing on the wall behind, plus a nearby scale buck\"\n<reflection_read> ::= \"striped reflection boards and ceiling light lines reading across the clay to reveal surface highlights and flaws\"\n<repro> ::= \"a photographic studio shot, controlled overhead lighting for surface read, neutral studio, no dark-field drama\"\n\n[instruction]\nmodel input_topic's signature form as an in-progress full-scale design-studio clay — taped section\nlines, half di-noc, wall tape-drawing, reflection boards revealing the surface. clinical and unfinished, not a hero product.",
      "prompt_ko": "영화/게임/만화의 상징적 탈것·오브젝트를 '자동차 디자인 스튜디오의 미완성 실물크기 클레이 모델'로 재현하는 BNF 문법 프롬프트. 절반은 매트 클레이, 절반은 디녹 필름 마감 미리보기, 벽엔 테이프 도면, 줄무늬 반사판으로 표면 굴곡 체크 — '완성된 히어로 제품'이 아니라 '작업 중인 프로토타입'을 그리는 게 핵심. input_topic만 바꿔 재사용.",
      "gen_prompt": "An X-wing starfighter modeled as an in-progress full-scale design-studio clay prototype. A design-studio floor with a turntable and a tool board of clay rakes and slicks. The X-wing's hero form rendered as a full-scale matte styling-clay model, taped section lines across its surfaces. Di-noc film wraps one half of the model to preview the finished paint and glazing. A full-size profile tape drawing on the wall behind, plus a nearby scale buck. Striped reflection boards and ceiling light lines read across the clay to reveal surface highlights and flaws. Photographic studio shot, controlled overhead lighting for surface read, neutral studio, no dark-field drama. Clinical and unfinished, not a hero product.",
