      "title": "일식 파인다이닝 스타더스트 광고 — 블루블랙×레드 포인트 (Oulaolao)",
      "prompt": "Create an ultra-premium cinematic food advertising poster for Oulaolao Japanese cuisine, designed as a cold blue-black fine-dining composition where only a small amount of vivid red ingredients illuminate the dark space like precious stars. The image should feel luxurious, restrained, atmospheric, and visually hypnotic, like a top-tier omakase campaign photographed as a celestial culinary moment. The upper space must be filled with ultra-fine seasoning dust, mist, and particle flow so delicate and luminous that it feels like stardust suspended in cold air.\n\nMain composition: vertical composition with the plated Japanese dish resting low in the frame on a dark ceramic plate or shallow bowl. The lower section feels grounded and elegant, while the upper section opens into a deep blue-black atmosphere filled with fine floating particles and cold mist. The food remains mostly centered and stable, with only a few ingredients and micro garnish elements gently lifted upward.\n\nFood direction: luxurious Japanese cuisine plating with refined sashimi or cold-dish sensibility — silky raw fish, subtle green herbs, delicate garnish, tiny citrus or micro accents, and a few vivid red ingredients used sparingly as luminous focal sparks (cherry-tomato-like accents, roe-like pearls, red garnish spheres), glowing against the cool dark space.\n\nColor strategy: deep cold tones — blue-black, deep navy, charcoal, cold mist white, silvery highlights — with only a small number of vivid red food accents as visual ignition points, like embers or stars in darkness.\n\nIngredient realism pushed to an extreme level: wet seafood sheen, silky fish texture, micro water droplets, knife-cut precision, cool reflective highlights, fresh herb fibers, delicate surface gloss.\n\nStardust particle effect (most important visual layer): fill the upper and middle space with extremely fine airborne seasoning dust, salt-like micro particles, condensation haze, and tiny luminous specks that behave like stardust, delicately illuminated by backlight, forming a soft cosmic field around the dish.\n\nMist and transparency: thin cold vapor and translucent culinary haze around the plate, catching the backlight and contributing to a sense of air and distance.\n\nLighting: strong cinematic backlight combined with soft side light, making the particle cloud shimmer like stardust, creating glowing edges on the red ingredients.\n\nSpatial depth: strong depth from foreground to background, some particles and red accents close to the viewer, others fading into the blue-black distance.\n\nPlate styling: premium dark ceramic plate or shallow bowl with matte, subtly textured finish. Background deep blue-black and softly atmospheric, no clutter, no visible setting.\n\nTypography minimal and premium: \"Oulaolao\", optional support line \"Japanese Cuisine\", subtle and secondary.\n\nMood: luxurious, celestial, restrained, cinematic, cold, precise, luminous, atmospheric, high-end omakase, elegant, hypnotic, ultra-premium, world-class food campaign quality.\n\nRendering: hyper-realistic commercial food photography, ultra-detailed Japanese cuisine plating, strong cinematic backlight, ultra-fine stardust-like seasoning particles, cold vapor and condensation haze, deep spatial layering, vivid red ingredient accents against blue-black space, premium dark ceramic plate, fine-dining editorial quality, 8k, masterpiece.\n\nNegative prompt: warm steam, heavy powder clouds, too many red ingredients, chaotic explosion, flat composition, low-detail seafood, cartoon particles, cheap restaurant poster, cluttered background, weak backlight, muddy colors, plastic-looking ingredients, poor depth, messy garnish.",
      "prompt_ko": "차갑고 짙은 블루블랙 파인다이닝 배경에 극소량의 선명한 붉은 식재료만 별처럼 빛나는 일식 광고 포스터. 상단은 조미료 가루·냉기 안개가 스타더스트처럼 부유하는 게 핵심 레이어, 접시는 하단에 안정적으로 배치. 강한 백라이트로 입자와 붉은 포인트를 반짝이게 하고, 절제된 타이포로 브랜드명만 살짝.",
