      "prompt": "Act as the Global Automotive Creative Director for Maruti Suzuki. Campaign: OWN THE CITY, Instagram, 4:5 vertical, 8K. Hero vehicle: latest-generation Indian Maruti Suzuki Swift, factory-correct proportions, OEM alloy wheels, authentic LED DRLs, correct grille, original badging, realistic paint reflections (Luster Blue / Sizzling Red / Pearl Arctic White). Location: modern Gurugram Cyber City, wide urban boulevard, glass skyscrapers, clean roads after light rain, morning blue hour into sunrise. Story: Swift pauses at an architectural intersection after an early morning drive, wet road reflecting warm sunlight. Composition: top=small Maruti Suzuki logo + editorial headline 'OWN THE CITY.', center=Swift ~70% of frame, three-quarter front angle, low camera, bottom=minimal spec panel (1.2L Z-Series / Agile Performance / Smart Hybrid) + CTA 'Book a Test Drive →', Swiss Grid alignment. Graphic design: Swiss Grid, subtle city-grid overlays, street map coordinates, road lane graphics. Colour system: Maruti Suzuki Blue/White/Black primary, Graphite/Concrete Grey/Urban Silver secondary, Electric Blue/Subtle Red/Minimal Chrome accent. Lighting: blue hour into sunrise, soft city reflections, premium automotive commercial lighting. Camera: Phase One XF IQ4 150MP, Schneider Kreuznach 80mm LS, low position, medium-format realism. Material detail: metallic paint flakes, tyre texture, glass reflections, wet asphalt. Colour grading: Kodak Vision3 cinematic response, luxury contrast. Reject generic automotive renders, floating vehicles, cheap CGI, fake speed effects, AI-generated automotive clichés.",
      "prompt_ko": "마루티 스즈키 글로벌 크리에이티브 디렉터로서, 신형 스위프트(Epic New Swift)의 젊은 도시 감성을 담은 인스타그램용 'OWN THE CITY' 캠페인 광고. 4:5 세로, 8K. 최신 인도형 스위프트(정확한 공장 비율·순정 알로이휠·LED DRL·정품 배지)를 구루그램 사이버시티의 유리 스카이스크레이퍼 대로에서 촬영, 이른 아침 비 갠 도로에 블루아워→일출 전환광. 상단=소형 로고+헤드라인 'OWN THE CITY.', 중앙=차량이 화면의 약 70% 차지·3/4 정면 앵글·로우 카메라, 하단=미니멀 스펙 패널+시승신청 CTA, 스위스 그리드 정렬. 컬러시스템·조명·카메라(Phase One 미디엄포맷)·재질 디테일까지 전부 명시된 완결형 프롬프트. 제네릭 자동차 렌더·공중부양 차량·값싼 CGI·가짜 스피드 이펙트 배제.",
      "gen_prompt": "A flagship Instagram social media advertisement for the all-new Maruti Suzuki Swift, campaign 'OWN THE CITY', 4:5 vertical, 8K ultra high resolution luxury commercial automotive photography. The latest-generation Indian Maruti Suzuki Swift in Sizzling Red, factory-correct proportions, OEM alloy wheels, authentic LED DRLs, correct grille, original badging, realistic paint reflections, perfect panel gaps, visible tyre sidewall texture. Location: modern Gurugram Cyber City, a wide urban boulevard lined with glass skyscrapers and contemporary architecture, clean roads after light rain with natural reflections, a modern pedestrian bridge, minimal traffic, morning blue hour transitioning into sunrise, optimistic atmosphere. The Swift pauses briefly at an architectural intersection, the road still slightly wet, warm sunlight reflecting from surrounding glass buildings. Composition: top has a small minimal Maruti Suzuki logo and an editorial headline 'OWN THE CITY.'; center shows the Swift occupying approximately 70% of the frame at a three-quarter front angle from a low camera perspective with strong leading lines, urban architecture framing the vehicle; bottom has a minimal specification panel reading '1.2L Z-Series / Agile Performance / Smart Hybrid' with a small CTA 'Book a Test Drive →', all in Swiss Grid alignment with perfect spacing. Modern editorial automotive layout with subtle city-grid overlays, street map coordinates, road lane graphics, small navigation markers, clean geometric divisions, no unnecessary decoration. Colour system: Maruti Suzuki Blue, white, and black as primary, graphite and concrete grey as secondary, electric blue and subtle chrome as accent. Lighting: blue hour into sunrise, soft city reflections, controlled highlights, premium automotive commercial lighting, natural HDR, realistic glass reflections. Shot as if with a Phase One XF IQ4 150MP medium-format camera, low camera position, true-to-life perspective with no exaggerated wide-angle distortion. Material detail: visible metallic paint flakes, fine tyre texture, crystal-clear LED optics, glass reflections, wet asphalt reflections. Colour grading: premium commercial automotive grading, cool city blues, warm sunrise highlights, neutral whites, deep blacks, cinematic luxury contrast. Global campaign quality, editorial automotive photography, no generic automotive renders, no floating vehicles, no cheap CGI, no fake speed effects.",
