      "prompt": "Create an elegant, premium travel poster featuring a magical miniature world of [COUNTRY/CITY/DESTINATION] emerging from the luminous smoke of an ornate antique brass magic lamp placed at the bottom right. The smoke transforms into a floating island-like diorama carved from paper, stone, and marble, showcasing the destination's iconic landmarks, traditional architecture, landscapes arranged along cliffs, terraces, staircases, bridges, plazas, temples, villages, castles. Foreground resembles paper sculpture, carved limestone, origami geometry, miniature architectural models. Background dissolves into a traditional East Asian ink wash (sumi-e) landscape with delicate watercolor gradients, mist-covered mountains. Include a tiny lone traveler near the lamp looking upward. Museum-quality vintage travel poster composition, warm textured parchment paper, floating diorama in upper two-thirds, lower third clean for typography. Palette: warm ivory, parchment white, sandstone, cream, soft sepia, muted ochre, restrained regional accent colors. Soft cinematic lighting.",
      "prompt_ko": "우아한 프리미엄 여행 포스터, [나라/도시/목적지]의 마법 같은 미니어처 세계가 우측 하단 정교한 앤티크 황동 마법램프의 빛나는 연기에서 피어오름. 연기가 종이·석재·대리석으로 조각된 떠 있는 섬 형태 디오라마로 변신, 목적지의 아이코닉 랜드마크·전통 건축·지형이 절벽·테라스·계단·다리·광장·사원·마을·성곽을 따라 유기적으로 배치. 전경은 페이퍼 스컬프처·조각석회암·오리가미 지오메트리·미니어처 건축모형의 정교한 융합. 배경은 동양 수묵(sumi-e) 산수화로 서서히 용해, 안개 낀 산과 섬. 램프 옆에 위를 올려다보는 작은 여행자 한 명. 뮤지엄급 빈티지 여행포스터 구도, 따뜻한 텍스처 양피지, 디오라마는 상단 2/3, 하단 1/3은 타이포용 여백. 팔레트=아이보리/파치먼트화이트/샌드스톤/크림/세피아+지역별 절제된 악센트컬러. (플레이스홀더를 교토로 구체화한 gen_prompt)",
      "gen_prompt": "An elegant, premium travel poster featuring a magical miniature world of Kyoto, Japan emerging from the luminous golden smoke of an ornate antique brass magic lamp placed at the bottom right. The smoke gradually transforms into a floating island-like diorama carved from paper, stone, and marble, seamlessly blending fantasy with authentic Japanese architecture. The miniature world showcases Kyoto's iconic landmarks: a vermilion torii gate arcade winding up a hillside, a multi-tiered wooden pagoda, traditional machiya townhouses with lattice windows, a golden pavilion reflected in a still pond, terraced bamboo groves, arched stone bridges over a koi stream, and a small stone garden with raked gravel, all arranged organically along dramatic terraces, staircases, and bridges, every structure handcrafted and highly detailed. The foreground resembles an exquisite fusion of paper sculpture, carved limestone, folded origami geometry, and finely chiseled marble, with intricate textures, tiny windows, winding staircases, courtyards, cherry blossom trees, small boats, and architectural ornaments. The background dissolves into a traditional East Asian ink wash sumi-e landscape painted with delicate watercolor gradients, expressive ink brushstrokes, soft atmospheric perspective, mist-covered mountains, distant pine trees, and subtle washes of monochromatic sepia and charcoal. The smoke from the lamp swirls upward with glowing golden particles before transforming into clouds, cliffs, and architecture, feeling ethereal and wonder-inducing. A tiny lone traveler in a simple cloak stands near the lamp, looking upward toward the floating world. Refined museum-quality vintage travel poster composition with generous negative space on warm textured parchment paper, the floating diorama occupying the upper two-thirds of the canvas, the lower third clean for typography. Color palette dominated by warm ivory, parchment white, sandstone, cream, soft sepia, and muted ochre, with restrained Japanese vermilion as the regional accent color. Soft cinematic lighting, gentle volumetric illumination, delicate rim lighting, subtle haze, soft painterly shadows. Masterpiece, ultra-detailed, paper sculpture, carved marble, sumi-e ink wash, parchment paper texture, magical realism, museum-quality illustration, luxury travel poster, 8k, editorial design.",
