      "prompt": "STORY:\n[SHORT STORY]\n\nCreate ONE cinematic storyboard.\n\nSilently identify the emotional progression.\n\nDivide into exactly six sequential frames.\n\nEach frame should show:\n• Camera angle\n• Subject action\n• Lighting\n• Environment\n• Emotion\n\nSTYLE:\nProfessional film previsualization, cinematic framing, realistic lighting, clean composition.\n\nAvoid:\ntext bubbles, unnecessary props, inconsistent characters.\n\nFinal output:\nOne storyboard page.",
      "prompt_ko": "임의의 짧은 이야기를 입력하면, 감정 흐름을 스스로 파악해 정확히 6개의 연속 프레임으로 나눈 한 장짜리 시네마틱 스토리보드를 생성하는 템플릿. 각 프레임은 카메라 앵글·인물 행동·조명·환경·감정을 담음. 프로페셔널 영화 프리비주얼라이제이션 스타일, 텍스트 말풍선·불필요한 소품·캐릭터 불일치 금지.",
      "gen_prompt": "A single cinematic storyboard page divided into six sequential rectangular panels (3 columns x 2 rows), professional film previsualization style, the same woman and setting kept fully consistent across all six frames, clean realistic lighting, no text bubbles or captions inside the panels. Story: a woman in her thirties returns alone to her childhood home after many years away. Panel 1 — wide establishing shot, she stands at the gate looking up at the weathered house, overcast late-afternoon light, apprehensive stillness. Panel 2 — medium shot from behind as she pushes open the front door into a dust-covered hallway, soft diagonal light through a cracked window, quiet hesitation. Panel 3 — close-up on her hand tracing a height chart pencil-marked on a doorframe, warm nostalgic side-light, tender curiosity. Panel 4 — over-the-shoulder shot as she sits on the floor of an empty room with a box of old photographs open in her lap, single window light, gentle sadness. Panel 5 — close-up on her face, eyes glistening with a faint smile breaking through, golden-hour light streaming in, quiet emotional release. Panel 6 — wide shot from outside through the window as she stands and walks toward the light, dusk settling outside, calm resolve. Realistic lighting continuity, clean uncluttered composition, muted natural color palette, thin hairline panel dividers, no prop inconsistency, no text overlays — pure visual storytelling.",
