      "prompt_ko": "클래식 오프로드 차량이 진흙탕을 가르는 다이나믹한 로우앵글 히어로샷 + 탐사장비(루프랙·연료캔·윈치·스노클 등) 완전무장 + 산/사막/사바나 배경에 거대한 황금빛 태양 + 1970~90s 빈티지 매거진 광고 질감(색바램·인쇄그레인) + 초대형 컨덴스드 타이포(차종명·연도) + 기술사양 패널·나침반·등고선맵·시리얼넘버·바코드·모험 슬로건(\"Built for the Wild\" 등)까지 갖춘 콜렉터블급 빈티지 원정 광고 포스터 템플릿.",
      "gen_prompt": "An ultra-detailed vintage overland expedition poster featuring a legendary classic off-road vehicle in a dramatic low-angle hero shot, charging powerfully through rugged dirt terrain while mud, dust, rocks, and debris explode beneath the oversized all-terrain tires. The vehicle is fully equipped for long-distance expedition travel with an expedition roof rack, spare tire, fuel jerry cans, recovery boards, a shovel, an axe, rooftop cargo, an LED light bar, a snorkel, a heavy-duty steel front bumper, an electric winch, D-ring shackles, a skid plate, rock sliders, lifted suspension, and aggressive off-road tires. The backdrop showcases a breathtaking wilderness landscape with towering mountains, rolling hills, desert or savannah scenery, scattered acacia trees, dramatic clouds, and an enormous glowing golden-orange sun dominating the horizon, creating a cinematic adventure atmosphere. Designed as a premium retro automotive travel poster with distressed vintage paper texture, subtle print grain, faded ink, a muted earthy color palette, and classic expedition magazine aesthetics inspired by 1970s-1990s outdoor adventure advertisements. The composition includes bold oversized condensed typography displaying the vehicle model at the top, the production year and country beneath it, technical specification panels, expedition icons, a compass rose, contour topographic map lines, coordinate markings, a serial edition number, a barcode, adventure badges, minimalist infographic elements, and a rugged motivational slogan such as 'Built for the Wild' or 'Conquer Any Terrain'. Hyper-detailed automotive illustration, cinematic lighting, dramatic perspective, crisp mechanical details, realistic mud splashes, ultra-sharp rendering, symmetrical editorial layout, premium adventure branding, collectible wall-art quality, 8k resolution, no people, no watermark.",
