      "title": "2x2 그리드 4인 운동복 캠페인 포스터 — 오버사이즈 에디토리얼 타이포 (시리즈 7편)",
      "prompt": "4-Square Grid High-End Fitness Apparel Collection 7\n\nGPT- image 2 prompt:\nCreate the seventh poster in a unified campaign series for Lululemon Athletica, designed as a bold four-panel editorial sports poster with four different athlete characters, four distinct movement themes, minimalist backgrounds, large graphic typography, and refined hand-drawn illustrated motifs that interact narratively with each figure. Hyper-real, visually explosive, fashion-forward, premium, clean structured 2x2 grid composition.\n\nOverall layout: vertical 4-panel grid, four equal quadrants. Each panel: different athlete, different movement posture, different emotional theme, but all four clearly belong to the same campaign family — a contemporary fashion-sport magazine cover system merged with avant-garde brand advertising.\n\nCritical series rule — all four panels share the same visual DNA: minimal background, bold editorial typography, realistic apparel, strong figure-to-text interaction, fine hand-drawn motifs, clean negative space, premium campaign polish. Each panel unique, but coherent, intentionally art-directed.\n\nColor system: cobalt blue, vivid orange, ivory white, graphite black, small accents of pale sky blue or muted warm gray. Fresh, youthful, energetic, modern, cleaner and more graphic than previous series entries.\n\nPanel 1: powerful athletic female figure in dynamic extended motion (long stride/twist/reach), strong diagonals, body elongation. Minimal bright background, oversized typography, hand-drawn motion streaks interacting with limbs.\nPanel 2: cool dominant low-angle figure stepping toward viewer, exaggerated perspective, street-fashion athletic confidence. Large bold text wraps around figure, intersecting the silhouette. Subtle illustrated symbols reinforcing impact/strength/balance.\nPanel 3: jumping/landing/mid-transition pose, energy and lift. Airy composition, large modern text blocks, delicate hand-drawn linework echoing the movement path. Uplifting mood.\nPanel 4: sculptural heroic pose from low/upward angle, climax panel. Typography more immersive, large letters interacting aggressively with the athlete, fine illustrated accents suggesting force/breath/momentum.\n\nAthletes: mix of healthy Western male and female athletic models, realistic anatomy, sculpted but believable physiques, high-fashion sports presence. No influencer look, no anatomy distortion.\n\nWardrobe: authentic premium performance apparel every panel — technical tanks, sports bras, lightweight performance jackets, training tops, tailored joggers, leggings, shorts, premium sneakers. Realistic folds, stretch tension, seam construction, matte performance surfaces. Cobalt-blue and vivid-orange distributed across styling, balanced with black/ivory/graphite.\n\nTypography: oversized English editorial words integrated deeply into each panel, letters partially behind/beside/around athletes. Directions: \"LULULEMON\" / \"ATHLETICA\" / \"MOVE LOUD\" / \"FORM IN MOTION\" / \"POWER TAKES SPACE\" / \"STRETCH THE FRAME\". Bold, modern, artistic, premium hierarchy.\n\nIllustration: fine hand-drawn motion arcs, energy streaks, wind lines, wave forms, abstract petals, graphic sparks, calligraphic swirls matched to each panel's movement theme — refined and integrated, never cartoonish.\n\nBackground: minimal, slight tonal variation, clean sky-like or studio-like openness, no cluttered environments.\n\nLighting: bright premium editorial lighting sculpting muscles/posture/fabric/footwear, each panel slightly different mood within the same premium system.\n\nMood: explosive, athletic, youthful, avant-garde, editorial, premium, modern, graphic, high-energy.\n\nNegative prompt: messy collage, inconsistent panel style, cluttered backgrounds, cheap fitness ad, weak typography, distorted anatomy, broken limbs, bad hands, extra fingers, twisted joints, influencer look, generic sportswear, low-detail fabric, cartoon doodles, chaotic layout, muddy colors, low-end poster design, blurry shoes, dirty shadows, black blotches",
      "prompt_ko": "동일 캠페인 시리즈 7번째 편 — 4인 운동선수를 2x2 그리드 4패널에 각기 다른 동작 테마로 배치한 에디토리얼 스포츠 포스터. 배치40(그래피티 타이포, 에메랄드그린, 단일인물)과 달리 이번엔 오버사이즈 에디토리얼 타이포(그래피티체 아님)+코발트블루/비비드오렌지 팔레트+4인 그룹. 패널마다 고유 동작(연장동작/로우앵글도발/점프이행/영웅적피날레)과 손그림 모션라인이 매칭됨. Krea2용 gen_prompt는 브랜드명 반복 없이 일반화.",
      "gen_prompt": "A bold four-panel editorial sports campaign poster in a clean 2x2 grid, hyper-real, fashion-forward, premium. Four different athletic models, four distinct movement themes, minimal backgrounds, oversized graphic typography, and refined hand-drawn illustrated motifs interacting narratively with each figure — a contemporary fashion-sport magazine cover system merged with avant-garde brand advertising. All four panels share the same visual DNA (minimal background, bold editorial typography, realistic premium activewear, strong figure-to-text interaction, fine hand-drawn motifs, clean negative space) while each panel stays unique. Color system: cobalt blue, vivid orange, ivory white, graphite black, with small accents of pale sky blue or muted warm gray — fresh, youthful, energetic, modern. Panel 1: a powerful athletic female figure in dynamic extended motion (long stride, twist, or reach) with strong diagonals; oversized typography and hand-drawn motion streaks interact with her limbs. Panel 2: a cool, dominant low-angle male or female figure stepping toward the viewer with street-fashion confidence; large bold text wraps around and intersects the silhouette. Panel 3: a jumping or mid-transition pose capturing lift and rhythm, airy composition, large modern text blocks, delicate hand-drawn linework echoing the movement path. Panel 4: a sculptural heroic pose from a low upward angle as the climax panel, typography interacting aggressively with the athlete, fine illustrated accents suggesting force and momentum. Athletes have realistic anatomy and believable athletic physiques, no distortion. Premium technical activewear — tanks, sports bras, lightweight jackets, tailored joggers, leggings, premium sneakers — rendered with realistic fabric stretch and seam detail. Bold editorial wordmarks such as 'MOVE LOUD', 'FORM IN MOTION', or 'POWER TAKES SPACE'. Bright premium editorial lighting sculpting muscle, posture, and fabric detail. Mood: explosive, athletic, youthful, avant-garde, editorial, high-energy. Avoid: messy collage, inconsistent panel style, cluttered backgrounds, distorted anatomy or bad hands, generic sportswear, cartoon doodles, chaotic layout, muddy colors.",
      "result": "results/ou-zhen599-4panel-grid-fitness-campaign-7.png",
