      "lang": "en",
      "target_model": "GPT Image 2 (SDF 셰이더 의사코드 템플릿)",
      "category": "미니어처/그리드",
      "title": "책 속 세계 — 구체 컷어웨이 미니어처 디오라마 (SDF 셰이더 의사코드, 4권 2x2 그리드)",
      "prompt": "A fun way to visualize books, even poems and movies if you can get them past GPT's restrictions.\n\nPrompt:\n2x2 grid, 16:9, do this for 4 non copyrighted, public space books\n// Sphere SDF\nfloat sdf_sphere = sdSphere(p, 1.0);\n// Crack: a noise-modulated cutting plane that splits the sphere\nfloat crack = fbm(p) > 0.5 ? 1.0 : 0.0; // left/right\n// Outer left shell: displace sdf slightly for manuscript relief, then shade with cultural texture.\nfloat sdf_exterior = sdf_sphere; // left side only\n// Interior: carve a hollow region by subtracting a smaller sphere offset, leaving a shell.\nfloat sdf_cavern = sdSubtract(sdf_sphere, sdSphere(p - vec3(0.4,0,0), 0.8)); // hollow right side\n// Tiered architecture: series of nested boxes and cylinders placed along the cavern walls\nfloat sdf_arch = tiered_structures(p, epic_cities);\n// Creatures: SDFs of mythical beasts placed dynamically.\nfloat sdf_river = thin_tube(p, epic_river_path);\n// Soldiers: instanced tiny humanoid SDFs with armor, in formations.\n// Materials: manuscript = diffuse + normal map from calligraphy brush strokes; architecture = stone/gold PBR; interior light = emissive fire.\n// Lighting: point light deep inside cavern (fire), area light for studio.\n// Camera: macro lens, f/2.0, focus on cavern middle, DOF blur background and outer shell edges.\n// Post: shallow DOF, white studio beyond sphere, no modern elements.",
      "prompt_ko": "책(또는 시·영화)을 '반으로 갈라진 구체' 형태로 시각화하는 SDF(signed distance function) 셰이더 의사코드 템플릿. 구체 왼쪽 절반=원작 필사본 텍스처가 새겨진 외피, 오른쪽 절반=속을 파낸 공동(空洞)으로 그 안에 작품 속 세계(계단식 건축물·신화 생물이 사는 가는 강줄기·갑옷 입은 병사 대형)가 미니어처로 들어있는 구조. 내부는 불빛(emissive fire), 외부는 스튜디오 백색광. 매크로렌즈+얕은 심도로 공동 중앙에 포커스. 저작권 없는(퍼블릭 도메인) 책 4종을 2x2 그리드로.",
      "gen_prompt": "A macro studio photograph of a sphere sliced cleanly in half, revealing a miniature world inside — visualizing Homer's The Odyssey. The left exterior half of the sphere is an aged manuscript shell, its surface carved in subtle relief with ancient Greek calligraphy and faded ink texture, like a page grown into stone. The right half is hollowed into a glowing interior cavern: tiered ancient Greek architecture — stepped marble temples and stacked hillside dwellings — lines the cavern walls, receding into the depth. A thin winding river cuts through the miniature landscape, a serpentine sea-monster coiling along its length. Tiny bronze-armored soldier figures stand in formation on a terrace overlooking the river, rendered with fine handcrafted detail. The interior glows with warm firelight emanating from deep within the cavern, casting long dramatic shadows across the miniature architecture, while the exterior manuscript shell is lit by soft neutral studio light. Shot on a macro lens at f/2.0, focus locked on the cavern's middle depth, with shallow depth of field softly blurring the background and the outer shell's edges. Pure white studio background beyond the sphere, no modern elements, timeless mythic atmosphere, ultra-detailed miniature diorama craftsmanship.",
      "result": "results/gdgtify-sdf-sphere-book-world-cutaway.png",
