      "prompt": "GPT image 2 on ChatGPT\n\nCreate a stylish modern travel poster inspired by risography about DUBAI. Use simplified illustrated images of the city: the Gwanganje Bridge, ocean waves, seagulls, beach umbrellas, fish baskets at the market, neon street signs and small abstract decorative figures. Create a bold, multi-layered risographic poster with imperfect ink design, translucent colors printed on top, graininess in semitones, rough paper texture, flat graphic shapes, playful geometric shapes, and energetic editorial composition. Use fluorescent pink, bright blue, warm yellow, orange-red, leafy green, and rich cobalt blue on a white paper background. Add bold font in English: Main title: \"DUBAI\" A subtitle describing the city. The text in the footer: \"ARTISTIC PRINTING · COASTAL STORIES · 2026\" The design should be bright, cultural, modern, playful and collectable, like the original independent risographic poster for a local creative festival. Avoid copying any existing poster, artist's style, corporate identity, logo, mascot, copyrighted character, exact layout, or recognizable commercial design. Create an original composition inspired only by risographic printing technologies and modern independent poster design.",
      "prompt_ko": "리소그래프(공판 인쇄) 질감의 인디 크리에이티브 페스티벌풍 여행 포스터. 단순화된 도시 랜드마크·바다·갈매기·파라솔·시장 어물바구니·네온간판을 형광핑크·브라이트블루·웜옐로·오렌지레드·리프그린·코발트블루로 겹쳐 인쇄, 불완전한 잉크·반투명 컬러겹침·거친 종이 질감. 메인타이틀+서브타이틀+푸터(\"ARTISTIC PRINTING · COASTAL STORIES · 2026\"). ⚠️원문에 지역명 오류 있음 — \"두바이\" 랜드마크로 \"Gwanganje Bridge\"(광안대교, 실제로는 부산 지명)를 언급함. 재사용 시 실제 대상 도시의 랜드마크로 교체 권장.",
      "gen_prompt": "A stylish modern travel poster inspired by risography, for Busan. Use simplified illustrated images of the city: the Gwangan Bridge, ocean waves, seagulls, beach umbrellas, fish baskets at the market, neon street signs, and small abstract decorative figures. A bold, multi-layered risographic poster with imperfect ink registration, translucent colors printed on top of each other, graininess in the semitones, rough paper texture, flat graphic shapes, playful geometric shapes, and an energetic editorial composition. Fluorescent pink, bright blue, warm yellow, orange-red, leafy green, and rich cobalt blue on a white paper background. Bold English typography: main title 'BUSAN', a short subtitle describing the city, and footer text reading 'ARTISTIC PRINTING · COASTAL STORIES · 2026'. Bright, cultural, modern, playful, and collectable, like an original independent risographic poster for a local creative festival — an original composition inspired only by risographic printing technology and modern independent poster design.",
