      "id": "derek-wall90176-materialized-explainer-diagram-template",
      "source": "https://x.com/derek_wall90176/status/2076841958191120440",
      "author": "Derek Wen",
      "date": "2026-07-14",
      "lang": "zh",
      "target_model": "GPT Image 2",
      "category": "인포그래픽",
      "title": "머티리얼화 설명도 템플릿 — 백색 스튜디오 3D 소재 + 단일 포인트컬러",
      "prompt": "生成一张“材质化解释图”。\n主题：【填写主题】 核心元素：【填写要解释的概念 / 结构 / 流程】\n图像风格： 白底工作室光线，物体摆放在白色桌面上，像真实实体模型摄影。 整体干净、克制、有高级感。\n核心元素采用轻量3D材质质感（磨砂塑料、半透明亚克力、金属、玻璃、纸质卡片等）。\n画面中只使用一个鲜明点缀色（IKB蓝、橙色、薄荷绿、马卡龙粉、亮黄色等）。\n其余部分保持白色、浅灰、黑色和低饱和中性色。\n请在图中嵌入简短中文标签（2—5个汉字），放在白色空间、标注板或细线指示区。\n整体要像： 杂志级知识解释图 高端PPT中心配图 产品说明模型 教育科普示意图 工作汇报里的概念可视化图\n要求：信息清楚、结构简洁、模块关系明确。 禁止复杂背景、多色堆叠、廉价科技感、过度装饰、标签变形。",
      "prompt_ko": "\"머티리얼화 설명도(材质化解释图)\" 템플릿 — 백색 스튜디오 조명 배경 위에 개념·구조·프로세스의 핵심 요소를 반투명 아크릴·무광 플라스틱·금속·유리·종이카드 같은 가벼운 3D 소재 오브젝트로 표현하고, 화면 전체에 딱 하나의 포인트컬러(IKB블루/오렌지/민트/마카롱핑크/브라이트옐로)만 사용, 나머지는 화이트·라이트그레이·블랙 등 저채도 뉴트럴. 짧은 2~5자 한자(현지화 시 한글) 라벨을 화이트 여백이나 얇은 지시선에 배치. 매거진급 지식해설도·고급 PPT 센터비주얼·제품설명 모형·교육용 인포그래픽 톤. ⚠️원문은 【填写主题】/【填写要解释的概念】 빈칸이 있는 템플릿이라 실제 생성 시 구체적 주제로 채워야 함(예시=커피 추출 과정).",
      "gen_prompt": "A 'materialized explanation diagram' about the process of brewing coffee. White studio background with soft even lighting, objects arranged on a clean white tabletop like real physical model photography — overall clean, restrained, and premium in feel. The core elements — coffee beans, a grinder, a paper filter/dripper, and a finished cup of coffee — are rendered with light 3D material textures: frosted matte plastic for the grinder body, translucent acrylic for the dripper cone, brushed metal for the scale, and soft matte ceramic for the cup. Use only ONE vivid accent color throughout the frame — a rich cobalt blue (IKB blue) — applied to a single connecting element such as the pour-over kettle or a thin guide line, while everything else stays white, light grey, black, and low-saturation neutral tones. Embed short Korean text labels (2 to 4 characters each) directly in the white space or on thin label boards/lines next to each object: '원두' (beans), '분쇄' (grind), '추출' (brew), '완성' (finish), arranged left to right to show the process flow. The overall look should resemble a magazine-quality explainer graphic, a premium PPT centerpiece visual, a product-instruction model shot, or an educational science diagram — clear information, simple structure, and obvious relationships between each stage. Avoid complex backgrounds, multiple competing colors, cheap sci-fi tech looks, over-decoration, or distorted/illegible labels.",
      "result": "results/derek-wall90176-materialized-explainer-diagram-template.png",
      "seed": 1337988736,
      "ref_image": null
