      "target_model": "GPT Image 2",
      "category": "제품 광고",
      "title": "미니멀 럭셔리 레트로 에디토리얼 포스터 — Common Projects 아킬레스 스니커즈",
      "prompt": "Create an ultra-premium editorial poster for Common Projects Achilles, centered on a hyper-real Common Projects Original Achilles Low sneaker as the absolute hero product. The image should reinterpret a retro graphic product-poster layout through the lens of Common Projects: minimal, refined, quiet, architectural, and luxuriously restrained. The composition must feel bold and collectible like a vintage poster, yet exceptionally clean, modern, and elevated, with the sneaker dominating the layout.\n\nUse a vertical poster composition with one oversized Common Projects Achilles sneaker placed prominently across the center, angled with sculptural clarity and strong product authority. Render the shoe with absolute realism:\nsmooth premium leather,\nprecise low-top silhouette,\nclean toe shape,\nrefined sole geometry,\nsubtle stitching,\nluxury finishing,\nand the iconic gold serial number stamp clearly visible on the side.\nThe shoe must feel unmistakably Common Projects: minimal, elegant, expensive, and perfectly made.\n\nVisual language:\nBuild the poster with retro-inspired graphic structure:\nlarge headline typography,\nframed text blocks,\nfine stripe elements,\nquiet circles,\nsmall repeated silhouette motifs,\nclean geometric containers,\nand subtle print-based layout rhythm.\nHowever, reinterpret all of these elements through Common Projects’ identity:\nmore minimal,\nmore precise,\nmore architectural,\nmore luxurious,\nless playful,\nless graphic noise,\nmore gallery-poster restraint.\n\nColor system:\nUse a refined Common Projects-appropriate retro palette:\nwarm ivory,\nsoft cream,\nbone white,\nstone beige,\nmuted taupe,\ncharcoal,\nsoft faded black,\nand restrained accents of dusty navy or muted terracotta if needed.\nKeep the palette calm, premium, and understated.\nAvoid loud sport colors or high-saturation pop tones.\n\nBackground and poster graphics:\nKeep the background flat, clean, and elegant with subtle paper texture or soft archival print grain. Add thoughtfully placed poster elements such as:\noversized word blocks,\nfine vertical or horizontal lines,\nquiet number systems,\nsmall product repeats,\nsubtle stamp-like marks,\nminimal circles,\nand clean boxed annotations.\nEverything must remain spacious, highly intentional, and visually disciplined.\n\nTypography:\nUse only elegant English typography.\nPossible headline directions:\n“COMMON PROJECTS”\n“ACHILLES”\n“ORIGINAL ACHILLES LOW”\n“THE ESSENTIAL FORM”\n“QUIET ICON”\nTypography must feel modern, editorial, and luxurious, with strong hierarchy and generous spacing. The layout should look like a collectible design poster rather than a commercial sports ad.\n\nBrand coding:\nIntegrate Common Projects brand identity in a refined way:\nminimal product naming,\ngold serial number emphasis,\nItalian-made craftsmanship cues,\nsubtle luxury annotation,\nand understated fashion documentation tone.\nDo not make it feel sporty, streetwear-heavy, or overdesigned.\n\nLighting:\nUse soft premium editorial lighting with delicate highlights across the leather upper, sole edge, heel tab, and stamped serial number. The lighting should feel controlled, gallery-like, and luxurious, allowing the shoe to remain hyper-real while the surrounding poster system stays flatter and print-like.\n\nMood:\nminimal, collectible, refined, architectural, luxurious, understated, retro-editorial, modern, quiet, premium.\n\nRendering style:\nhyper-real Common Projects Original Achilles Low sneaker, retro graphic poster layout, minimal luxury fashion branding, ivory and stone palette, clean editorial typography, subtle archival print texture, premium soft lighting, 8k, world-class campaign quality.\n\nNegative prompt:\ngeneric sneaker ad, sporty branding, loud colors, cartoon graphics, cluttered layout, plastic-looking leather, wrong Achilles silhouette, missing gold serial number, cheap poster texture, streetwear overload, messy typography, low-detail sole, fake luxury styling, overdecorated background",
      "prompt_ko": "Common Projects 아킬레스 로우 스니커즈를 초현실 렌더링한 히어로 프로덕트로 세로형 레트로 그래픽 포스터 레이아웃에 배치. 아이보리·소프트크림·본화이트·스톤베이지·머디토프 등 차분한 레트로 팔레트, 골드 시리얼 넘버 각인 강조, 대형 헤드라인 타이포(\"COMMON PROJECTS\"/\"ACHILLES\" 등)+가는 스트라이프·서클·박스형 인포그래픽 요소, 소프트 에디토리얼 조명. 스포티·스트리트웨어톤 배제, 갤러리 포스터급 절제미 지향.",
