      "title": "스토리북 디오라마 캐릭터 백과사전 — 오픈북 팝업 스프레드",
      "prompt": "2x2 grid, 16:9, do this for 4 famous scifi movies: {INPUT: $ SUBJECT\n\nA = {\n  open storybook diorama,\n  cute 3D character world,\n  warm clay/vinyl miniature materials,\n  labeled origin panels,\n  model-sheet side views,\n  accessory callouts,\n  collectible character design\n}\n\nB = {\n  dense illustrated encyclopedia,\n  tiny worldbuilding details,\n  micro-architecture,\n  miniature people / animals / objects,\n  hand-painted storybook charm,\n  inspectable hidden scenes\n}\n\nC = {\n  designer toy proportions,\n  rounded expressive faces,\n  cozy fantasy-adventure mood,\n  tactile handcrafted props,\n  organized page layout\n}\n\nSUBJECT_CORE = stylize($ SUBJECT)\nwhere:\n- preserve the main identity of $ SUBJECT\n- convert it into a charming collectible character, object, creature, building, or scene\n- simplify proportions into cute readable forms\n- make it feel like the hero of a storybook universe\n\nBOOK_WORLD = infer_world($ SUBJECT)\nwhere:\n- create an open book or field-guide spread\n- left page: title, origin, values, symbols, short quote, icons, tiny lore text\n- center: dimensional pop-up diorama of the subject's world\n- right page: model sheet, expressions, accessories, palette, material swatches\n- fill the world with small props, creatures, signs, tools, plants, and narrative fragments inferred from $ SUBJECT\n\nMATERIAL_FUSION:\n- character and props rendered as soft matte clay / vinyl / miniature sculpture\n- pages rendered as warm aged paper with printed labels and tiny diagrams\n- small details rendered with storybook illustration charm\n- environmental pieces built as handcrafted diorama objects\n\nCOLOR_RULES:\n- warm parchment base\n- cozy saturated accents\n- teal, ochre, coral, forest green, cream, clay brown, soft blue\n- avoid harsh neon or photorealistic material\n\nOUTPUT:\nA premium open-book character encyclopedia diorama for $ SUBJECT, combining toy design, storybook lore, miniature worldbuilding, and model-sheet clarity.}",
      "prompt_ko": "펼쳐진 책 형태의 팝업 디오라마 + 캐릭터 백과사전 스타일. $SUBJECT를 귀여운 컬렉터블 캐릭터/오브젝트로 단순화하고, 왼쪽 페이지=제목·기원·상징·짧은 로어 텍스트, 가운데=입체 팝업 디오라마, 오른쪽 페이지=모델시트·표정·소품·팔레트 스와치 구성. 클레이/비닐 피규어 질감+따뜻한 올드페이퍼 인쇄물 질감 혼합, 웜파치먼트 베이스+틸/오커/코랄/포레스트그린 등 코지 액센트. 원 트윗은 4개 SF영화를 2x2 그리드로 요청.",
      "gen_prompt": "An open storybook field-guide spread for 'a rain-soaked robot detective in a neon noir city', as a premium open-book character encyclopedia diorama combining toy design, storybook lore, miniature worldbuilding, and model-sheet clarity. The robot detective is stylized into a charming collectible character — simplified rounded proportions, an expressive face, a trench coat and a tiny magnifying-glass accessory — feeling like the hero of a storybook universe, rendered in soft matte clay/vinyl miniature-sculpture material. The left page shows a title, short lore text, an origin symbol, and small icons on warm aged paper with printed labels and tiny diagrams. The center of the spread rises as a dimensional pop-up diorama of the character's rainy neon-lit city world — miniature buildings, tiny umbrella-carrying citizens, a food cart, and glowing signage, all built as handcrafted diorama objects with storybook illustration charm. The right page is a model sheet: alternate expressions, accessory callouts (badge, magnifying glass, coat), a small color palette, and material swatches. Designer-toy proportions, rounded expressive faces, cozy fantasy-noir mood, tactile handcrafted props, organized page layout. Color palette: warm parchment base with cozy saturated accents of teal, ochre, coral, and soft blue — avoid harsh neon or photorealistic material.",
