      "title": "아이소메트릭 디자이너토이 저탄수 다이어트 디너파티 뷔페 플래너",
      "prompt": "2x2 grid, 16:9, do this for 4 low carb diets: render_target = ( isometric_mod_designer_toy_style_buffet_table_layout_for_a_[diet_type]_dinner_party_with_appetizer_main_dessert_drinks * 1.6 ) + ( menu_flow_and_timing_wheel_for_a_6-course_[diet_type]_feast * 1.5 ) + ( individual_dish_cards_for_each_course_with_macros_and_[diet_type]_compliance_check * 1.4 ) + ( allergen_and_cross_contamination_prevention_visual_for_[diet_type] * 1.2 ) + ( prep_schedule_timeline_from_2_days_before_to_serving * 1.3 ) + ( plating_and_presentation_sketch_for_each_[diet_type]_course * 1.1 ) + ( drink_pairing_flowchart_non_alcoholic_and_alcoholic_for_[diet_type] * 1.0 ) - ( judgment_about_other_diets_or_food_shaming / 3.6 ) - ( overly_restrictive_miserable_plates / 3.3 ) - ( generic_buffet_stock_photos_of_unlabeled_dishes / 3.1 )",
      "prompt_ko": "저탄수 식단(키토/팔레오 등)별 디너파티를 다루는 가중치 함수형 시밀 인포그래픽 프롬프트. 아이소메트릭 디자이너토이 스타일 뷔페 테이블 레이아웃(전채·메인·디저트·음료)에 6코스 메뉴 흐름/타이밍 휠, 코스별 매크로영양소+식단준수 체크 카드, 알레르겐/교차오염 방지 비주얼, 준비 2일전~서빙 타임라인, 코스별 플레이팅 스케치, 논알콜/알콜 페어링 플로우차트를 가중치로 합성. 음식 판단·수치심 유발, 지나치게 제한적인 초라한 플레이팅, 라벨 없는 일반 뷔페 스톡사진은 감산(회피) 요소로 명시.",
      "gen_prompt": "An isometric designer-toy-style infographic buffet scene for a keto dinner party. The centerpiece is an isometric miniature buffet table layout with clearly separated appetizer, main course, dessert, and drinks stations rendered in cute rounded designer-toy proportions and materials. Around it, arrange supporting infographic elements: a circular menu-flow-and-timing wheel for a 6-course keto feast showing course order and timing; individual dish cards for each course displaying macro nutrition breakdowns and a keto-compliance checkmark; a small allergen and cross-contamination prevention diagram; a prep-schedule timeline running from 2 days before the party to serving time; simple plating-and-presentation sketches for each course; and a drink-pairing flowchart covering both non-alcoholic and alcoholic options. Warm, appetizing, organized editorial infographic layout with clear labels on every dish — avoid any judgmental tone about other diets or food-shaming language, avoid overly restrictive or miserable-looking plates, and avoid generic unlabeled stock-photo-style buffet dishes. Bright, clean, inviting color palette suited to a designer-toy product-illustration aesthetic.",
