      "category": "일러스트 스타일",
      "title": "코지 스토리북 모닝 — 노르딕×일본 수채 일러스트 스타일",
      "prompt": "I found a Midjourney SREF that feels like a quiet storybook morning.\n\n--sref 3198759719 --niji 6\n\nIt blends Nordic minimalism, soft Japanese illustration, and a cozy vintage palette. Think warm beige, muted browns, gentle plants, tiny expressive characters, soft textures, and that calm \"children's book you never forgot\" feeling.\n\nWhat makes it work:\nsimple shapes, but not empty\nwarm colors, but not boring\ncute characters, but not childish\nhand-drawn texture, but still clean\n\nBest for:\nchildren's book illustrations\nwellness app visuals\ncafé and bookstore posters\ncozy lifestyle content\nbrand packaging with a warm handmade feel\ncalm social media illustrations\n\nPrompt words that make this style stronger:\ncozy fairytale style\nJapanese watercolor texture\nNordic minimalist design\nsoft beige and brown palette\ngentle natural elements\nhand-drawn vintage warmth\n\n※ 원 게시자는 '전체 프롬프트는 댓글/외부 링크에'라고만 언급 — 실제 전체 프롬프트 텍스트는 얻지 못함(외부 유료/가입 링크로 게이트됨). 위는 게시글 본문의 스타일 설명·키워드 전부.",
      "prompt_ko": "미드저니 SREF(스타일 레퍼런스 코드) 3198759719 + --niji 6 기반 스타일. 노르딕 미니멀리즘+부드러운 일본 수채 일러스트+코지 빈티지 팔레트(웜베이지·머디브라운) 혼합, 작고 표정있는 캐릭터, 부드러운 질감, \"잊지 못할 동화책\" 감성. 카페/서점 포스터·웰니스 앱 비주얼·브랜드 패키징 등에 추천. ⚠️sref 코드 자체는 미드저니 전용이라 GPT-image2/Krea2로 이식 불가 — 게시글의 스타일 서술+키워드만으로 재구성한 텍스트 프롬프트를 gen_prompt에 작성.",
      "gen_prompt": "A cozy storybook illustration in a style blending Nordic minimalism, soft Japanese watercolor illustration, and a warm vintage palette. A gentle morning scene — a small character reading by a window with a cup of tea, surrounded by potted plants and soft warm light. Warm beige and muted brown tones throughout, with tiny expressive characters rendered in simple, clean shapes that stay warm rather than empty, and cute proportions that read as charming rather than childish. Soft hand-drawn watercolor texture with visible paper grain, clean linework, gentle natural elements (leaves, small plants, soft clouds), and a calm 'children's book you never forgot' feeling. Nordic minimalist composition with generous breathing space, soft diffused lighting, cozy fairytale mood — suitable for a children's book illustration, café poster, or wellness brand visual.",
