      "title": "미니멀 흑백회색 '구도 참조 카드' 템플릿 — 포스터 제작 전 레이아웃 설계용",
      "prompt": "生成一张【画幅比例】极简黑白灰\"构图参考图\"，主题为【构图主题】，英文副标题为【英文标题】。整体气质像设计师的版式研究卡、构图草稿、视觉参考图，白底黑字浅灰图形，克制、轻盈、留白充足。\n\n这不是说明书，不要大段解释，不要步骤讲解，不要 how to use，不要信息过多。只保留少量文字：中文标题、英文副标题、1句短辅助文案、少量小字、日期【日期】、细线、小圆点、极简符号。\n\n标题位置必须根据【构图主题】变化，不要固定左上角。标题、图形、小字要共同参与构图。灰色块面要作为构图骨架，直接表达【构图逻辑关键词】。整体更像\"构图案例示例\"，而不是\"设计原则讲解页\"。\n\n风格倾向：【极简 / 瑞士平面 / 构成主义 / 设计草图】\n灰色图形类型：【圆形 / 椭圆 / 弧线 / 斜切块 / 分区块面 / 环绕路径】\n辅助短句：【辅助短句】\n\n避免：说明书感、教程感、信息过多、标题全堆左上、模板感过强、彩色、复杂装饰、AI乱码。",
      "prompt_ko": "포스터/커버/제안서를 만들기 전 '구도 자체'만 미리 참조카드로 뽑아보는 메타 디자인 템플릿. 흰 배경+검은 텍스트+옅은 회색 도형만 사용한 극미니멀 '디자이너 판형 연구 카드' 느낌, 설명서/튜토리얼 톤 절대 금지(정보 과다·좌상단 고정 타이틀·컬러·과한 장식 회피). 회색 블록이 구도의 뼈대 역할을 하며 시각적 논리(사선 장력·환포 주축·절단면 분할 등)를 직접 표현. 필드=화면비율·구도주제·영문부제·날짜·구도로직키워드·스타일성향(미니멀/스위스그래픽/구성주의/디자인스케치)·회색도형종류(원/타원/호/사선절단블록/분할블록/환포경로)·보조문구.",
      "gen_prompt": "Generate a 4:5 ultra-minimal black-white-grey 'composition reference card' on the theme of 'Diagonal Tension', with the English subtitle 'DIAGONAL TENSION'. The overall mood should feel like a designer's layout research card, a composition sketch, or a visual reference sheet — white background, black text, light grey graphic shapes, restrained, light, with generous negative space.\n\nThis is not an instruction manual — no long explanations, no step-by-step walkthrough, no 'how to use' text, no information overload. Keep only minimal text: the title 'DIAGONAL TENSION', one short supporting line reading 'Composition Before Content', a small amount of fine print, the date '2026.07', thin lines, a small dot, and minimal symbols.\n\nThe title position must vary according to the composition theme — do not default it to the top-left corner. Title, graphic shapes, and fine print must all participate in the composition together. The grey shape blocks act as the compositional skeleton, directly expressing 'diagonal potential energy' through diagonally-cut grey blocks sweeping across the frame. The overall feel should be like a 'composition case-study example', not a 'design-principles explainer page'.\n\nStyle leaning: minimalist, Swiss graphic design. Grey shape type: diagonal-cut blocks and zoned block divisions. Supporting short phrase: 'Composition Before Content'.\n\nAvoid: instruction-manual feel, tutorial feel, information overload, title stuck in the top-left, overly templated look, color, complex decoration, garbled AI text.",
