      "prompt": "2x2 grid, 16:9 do this for 4 famous cities around the world: . the crown jewel destination edition concept: the place is reimagined as the most luxurious collectible atlas object ever made — a ceremonial destination rendered like royal architecture emerging from a sacred volume. input variables: [insert place or region] [insert hero landmark] [insert supporting landmarks] [insert regional material symbolism] [insert sky iconography] [insert public life details] workflow: build a thick prestige book as the foundation for [insert place or region], styled like a collector's edition artifact. place [insert hero landmark] at the visual center as the crown jewel structure. arrange [insert supporting landmarks] around it with balanced grandeur, ensuring the composition feels dense but graceful. translate [insert regional material symbolism] into the sculptural treatment of the scene, while preserving a restrained white-and-gold luxury palette. suspend [insert sky iconography] above the miniature world as elegant decorative narrative elements. add roads, terraces, plazas, and transit lines that choreograph the viewer's eye across the book. fill plazas and streets with [insert public life details] at tiny scale for life and motion. expose ornate mechanical elements through page cutaways or side openings so the book feels like an engineered heirloom object. keep the scene pristine, ceremonial, and premium rather than messy or documentary. stage the entire piece like an ultra-high-end product photograph on a warm tabletop. god-level details: prestige collectible-object realism, royal atlas energy, white ceramic/paper monumentality, polished gold inlays, refined civic miniatures, gleaming clockwork ornament, luxury studio shadows, premium compositional symmetry, photoreal surface richness, 8k, thumbnail-stopping elegance.",
      "prompt_ko": "도시를 '역사상 가장 럭셔리한 수집용 아틀라스 오브제'로 재해석하는 템플릿 — 두꺼운 프레스티지 북(책) 형태 기단 위에 랜드마크가 왕실 건축물처럼 솟아오른 형상. 헤로 랜드마크는 중앙 크라운쥬얼로, 서브 랜드마크는 그 주위 균형있게 배치, 지역 소재 상징을 화이트+골드 팔레트의 조각적 표현으로 전환, 하늘엔 지역 아이코노그래피가 장식 요소처럼 떠있음. 도로·테라스·광장으로 시선유도, 광장엔 미니어처 인파, 페이지 컷어웨이로 정교한 태엽/기계장치 노출(마치 정밀공예 유물처럼). 따뜻한 조명의 초고급 제품사진 연출. 입력변수=지역/헤로랜드마크/서브랜드마크/지역소재상징/하늘아이콘/거리인파.",
      "gen_prompt": "The crown jewel destination edition concept for Seoul, South Korea: the city reimagined as the most luxurious collectible atlas object ever made — a ceremonial destination rendered like royal architecture emerging from a sacred volume. Build a thick prestige book as the foundation for Seoul, styled like a collector's edition artifact. Place Gyeongbokgung Palace at the visual center as the crown jewel structure, its dancheong-painted eaves and stone terraces rendered in sculptural white-and-gold relief. Arrange supporting landmarks — N Seoul Tower, the tiled rooftops of Bukchon Hanok Village, and a Han River bridge — around it with balanced grandeur, dense but graceful. Translate traditional Korean dancheong woodwork joinery and hanji paper texture into the sculptural treatment of the scene, preserving a restrained white-and-gold luxury palette throughout. Suspend paper cranes and glowing lanterns above the miniature world as elegant decorative narrative elements. Add roads, terraces, plazas, and a subway line that choreograph the viewer's eye across the book. Fill plazas and streets with tiny hanbok-wearing visitors and small street-food carts for life and motion. Expose ornate mechanical clockwork elements through page cutaways or side openings so the book feels like an engineered heirloom object. Keep the scene pristine, ceremonial, and premium rather than messy or documentary. Stage the entire piece like an ultra-high-end product photograph on a warm tabletop. God-level details: prestige collectible-object realism, royal atlas energy, white ceramic/paper monumentality, polished gold inlays, refined civic miniatures, gleaming clockwork ornament, luxury studio shadows, premium compositional symmetry, photoreal surface richness, 8k, thumbnail-stopping elegance.",
