      "title": "프로토타입 차량 추출 — 2x2 그리드 (함수형 의사코드 템플릿)",
      "prompt": "2x2 grid, 16:9,4 vehicles inspired by famous manga input = [vehicle_type / function / world_style / reference_image]\n\nrun prototype_vehicle_extraction:\n\nvehicle_dna := infer vehicle category, scale, role, terrain, speed, durability, and user interaction\nframe_system := infer exposed chassis, tubular frame, monocoque shell, exoskeleton, truss, cage, or modular platform\nbody_panel_system := infer armor plates, fairings, shells, panels, covers, aerodynamic surfaces, or protective geometry\npropulsion := infer engine, motor, wheels, tracks, rotors, jets, legs, sails, turbines, or hybrid system\ncontrol_position := infer rider, driver, pilot, operator, autonomous sensor stack, or remote-control logic\nmechanical_visibility := infer which components stay exposed versus covered\nmaterial_language := infer steel, aluminum, carbon fiber, plastic, rubber, composite, ceramic, wood, fabric, or fictional material\nsurface_finish := infer matte, raw metal, painted, dusty, welded, polished, carbon, patinated, weathered, or prototype primer\nbuild_context := infer garage, workshop, test track, roadside, lab, hangar, desert, shipyard, warehouse, or proving ground\ncamera_style := infer side-profile documentation, technical photo, hero render, field test shot, or build-progress image\n\nrender:\na realistic custom prototype vehicle with functional engineering logic and visible fabrication decisions.\n\nforbidden:\nhard-coded motorcycle, hard-coded matte black, hard-coded angular plates, hard-coded tires, random armor, impossible suspension, decorative fake mechanics.",
      "prompt_ko": "만화에서 영감 얻은 차량 4대를 2x2 그리드(16:9)로 뽑는 함수형 의사코드 템플릿. `run prototype_vehicle_extraction:` 아래 10개 슬롯을 모델이 스스로 추론(`:= infer`)하게 시킨다 — vehicle_dna(범주·스케일·역할·지형·속도·내구·조작), frame_system(노출 섀시/튜뷸러/모노코크/외골격/트러스/케이지/모듈러), body_panel_system(장갑판/페어링/쉘/공력면), propulsion(엔진·모터·바퀴·궤도·로터·제트·다리·돛·터빈), control_position(라이더/드라이버/파일럿/자율센서/원격), mechanical_visibility(노출 vs 은폐), material_language(강철·알루미늄·카본·복합재·목재·가상소재), surface_finish(무광·생메탈·도장·용접·파티나·프로토타입 프라이머), build_context(차고·작업장·테스트트랙·격납고·사막·조선소), camera_style(측면 도큐멘테이션/기술사진/히어로 렌더/필드테스트). 산출은 '기능적 엔지니어링 논리와 제작 흔적이 보이는 현실적 커스텀 프로토타입 차량'. forbidden 절로 모터사이클 고정·무광 검정 고정·각진 판 고정·타이어 고정·랜덤 장갑·불가능한 서스펜션·장식용 가짜 메커니즘을 금지. 저자 왈 영화·만화 주제에서 잘 작동. ※ 나노바나나(제미나이)·GPT Image 2 같은 LLM 기반 모델이 지시문을 추론하는 전제 — Krea2 등 확산 모델은 의사코드를 실행하지 못하고 특히 forbidden 목록을 부정으로 이해하지 못하므로, 아래 gen_prompt에서 4개 패널을 구체 서술로 풀어 재작성함. 원문 주제는 'famous manga'였으나 Krea2 재현 주제는 **블레이드 러너 2049**로 지정(스피너·농장 트럭·트래시메사 스캐빈저·월레스 스피너 — 호버제트·바퀴·궤도로 추진계가 갈리게 선정).",
      "gen_prompt": "A 2x2 grid of four custom prototype vehicles from a rain-soaked dystopian future, 16:9 widescreen, each panel a side-profile technical documentation photograph of a real fabricated machine with functional engineering logic and visible fabrication decisions. Top-left: a wedge-shaped armored police hover car, doors sealed, thick ribbed side panels over exposed thruster nacelles at the base, no wheels, hovering a few inches above a wet concrete pad with heat shimmer beneath, dark grey-blue paint over raw metal, worn edges and rain beading on the shell, glowing amber running lights. Top-right: a battered flatbed farm pickup on tall knobby tires, exposed tubular roll cage and welded brackets, dented steel body panels in faded ochre, mud-caked wheel arches and a cracked headlight, parked on grey volcanic soil beside a protein greenhouse. Bottom-left: a heavy tracked scavenger hauler with a slab-sided scrap-plate body, articulated steel tracks with visible drive sprockets and cable looms, a small armored cab set high with a sensor mast, patinated rust-brown and welded seams, standing in a wasteland of compacted refuse. Bottom-right: a sleek corporate executive hover limousine, a smooth monocoque shell of polished dark bronze with no visible seams, subtle aerodynamic surfaces and a concealed propulsion skirt, mirror finish reflecting a vast concrete hangar, immaculate and cold. Consistent lighting and camera height across all four panels, thin clean dividing lines between panels, muted teal-and-amber palette, heavy atmospheric haze, realistic materials with honest wear.",
      "result": "results/gdgtify-prototype-vehicle-extraction-grid.png",
