      "title": "과학 개념 4스타일 2x2 아트 그리드 (함수형 recommend(x) 템플릿)",
      "prompt": "One prompt that generates all kinds of visuals for scientific concepts. It's unpredictable, just how I like it.\n\nfunction recommend(x) {   let theory = Identify_Theory(x);   let concepts = Analyze_Scientific_Concepts(x);   let selection = Generate_4_Artistic_Representations(concepts) {       For each representation:           Random_Art_Style = Select_Random_Art_Style(); // e.g., abstract, surrealism, pop art           Represent(theory, Random_Art_Style);           Criteria: \"Thought-Provoking, Aesthetically Pleasing, Accurate\";   };   let grid_content = selection. map(art => {      let medium = Identify_Medium(art. Style);      let composition = Generate_Composition(art);      return Create_Artwork(art, medium, composition) {         Base: \"Digital painting or illustration\";         Style: art. Style;         Color_Palette: \"Based on the theory's properties (e.g., entanglement might use linking colors)\";         Elements: \"Symbolic representations of the theory\";         Texture: \"Mixed media if appropriate\";      };   });   return Generate_Image(2x2_Grid(grid_content)); }",
      "prompt_ko": "과학 개념(x)을 입력하면 4가지 랜덤 아트스타일로 표현한 2x2 그리드 이미지를 생성하는 함수형(JS 함수) 템플릿(Gdgtify). recommend(x) → 이론 식별 → 개념 분석 → 4개 아트 표현 생성(각기 랜덤 스타일: 추상·초현실·팝아트 등, 기준='사고를 자극·심미적·정확') → 각 아트워크(베이스=디지털 페인팅/일러스트, 스타일=랜덤, 컬러팔레트=이론 속성 기반[예: 얽힘=연결색], 요소=이론의 상징적 표현, 혼합매체 질감) → 2x2 그리드 이미지. ★함수형이라 재현 시 구체 이론(예: 양자얽힘)과 4개 스타일을 명시해 단일 2x2 그리드로 채움.",
      "gen_prompt": "A clean 2x2 grid of four artistic representations of the scientific concept of quantum entanglement, each panel in a different art style, thought-provoking, aesthetically pleasing and conceptually accurate.\nPanel 1 abstract geometric style: two interlinked particles connected by glowing threads, entanglement shown through paired mirrored forms and linking colors, deep blue and cyan.\nPanel 2 surrealism: two floating orbs joined across an impossible dreamscape, melting causality clocks, deep indigo and magenta.\nPanel 3 pop art: bold comic halftone dots, two bright particles wired together with electric linking lines, primary red-yellow-blue.\nPanel 4 art nouveau: elegant flowing linework weaving two entangled nodes into an ornamental symmetric pattern, gold and teal.\nDigital painting and mixed-media illustration, symbolic representations of quantum entanglement, linking color palette, mixed-media textures, balanced 2x2 grid composition, thin clean gutters between panels.",
