      "title": "히어로 → 마블 뮤지엄 액션 모뉴먼트 2x2 그리드 (함수형 $subject 템플릿)",
      "prompt": "Love making these manga prompts. Here is one that works well with Nano Banana Pro.\n\nprompt:2x2 grid, 16:9, do this for 4 famous mangas: concept anchor 1: \"museum marble action statue — white stone figures, dramatic combat pose, broken columns, floating debris, engraved plaques, gallery lighting\"\n\n::\n\nconcept anchor 2: \"aged sports legend poster — brush typography, ink portrait studies, motion diagrams, tactical arrows, paper grain, archival collage\"\n\n::\n\nconcept anchor 3: \"manga action concept sheet — explosive movement arcs, character close-up panels, speed effects, sketch annotations, intense heroic staging\"\n\ninstruction:\nfind the exact visual center of these three concepts.\nignore the specific characters, athletes, franchises, and events.\nextract only the style dna.\n\nrender $ subject as a legendary museum action monument documented like an archival hero poster.\n\nstyle rules:\n- the subject becomes a dynamic white marble or plaster sculpture frozen at peak action.\n- surround the sculpture with broken plinth fragments, floating debris, carved impact waves, and dramatic museum staging.\n- add an aged poster layer: brush-painted title, diagram arrows, inset close-ups, small motion studies, quotes, stamps, and technical notes.\n- use restrained color accents only for energy veins, motion paths, symbolic highlights, or key emotional impact.\n- keep the base material mostly ivory stone, gray marble, plaster dust, black ink, faded red, muted blue, ochre, and small neon cracks.\n- the composition should feel like a sacred sports shrine, manga battle study, and museum artifact fused into one.\n\noutput:\na heroic poster-monument of $ subject: carved in marble, annotated like a legend, and exploding with frozen action energy.",
      "prompt_ko": "히어로($ subject)를 대리석 뮤지엄 액션 모뉴먼트로 렌더링하는 함수형 템플릿(Gdgtify, Nano Banana Pro). 2x2 그리드 16:9. 3개 컨셉 앵커(①뮤지엄 대리석 액션 조각상 ②에이지드 스포츠 레전드 포스터[브러시 타이포·잉크 초상 스터디·모션 다이어그램·전술 화살표·종이 그레인·아카이브 콜라주] ③만화 액션 컨셉시트[폭발적 움직임 아크·캐릭터 클로즈업·스피드 이펙트·스케치 주석])의 '스타일 DNA'만 추출, 특정 캐릭터·프랜차이즈는 무시. 스타일 규칙=피사체를 피크 액션에서 얼어붙은 백색 대리석/플라스터 조각으로, 부서진 받침대 파편·부유 잔해·새겨진 임팩트 웨이브·드라마틱 뮤지엄 스테이징으로 둘러싸고, 에이지드 포스터 레이어(브러시 타이틀·다이어그램 화살표·인셋 클로즈업·모션 스터디·인용·스탬프·기술 노트) 추가. 절제된 컬러 액센트(에너지 베인·모션 패스·상징 하이라이트만), 베이스=아이보리 스톤·그레이 마블·플라스터·블랙잉크·페이디드 레드·뮤티드 블루·오커·소형 네온 크랙. '성스러운 스포츠 신전 + 만화 배틀 연구 + 뮤지엄 유물' 융합 인상. ★함수형이라 재현 시 $ subject를 오리지널 캐릭터로 채움(저작권 회피 — 원문도 특정 프랜차이즈 무시 지시).",
      "gen_prompt": "A 2x2 grid, 16:9, showing four different original legendary action heroes, each rendered as a museum marble action monument documented like an archival hero poster. Original characters only, no real franchise.\nEach panel: a dynamic white marble or plaster sculpture of the hero frozen at peak action, surrounded by broken plinth fragments, floating debris, carved impact waves, and dramatic museum gallery lighting. Over it an aged archival poster layer: brush-painted title, diagram arrows, inset close-up studies, small motion studies, quotes, stamps, and technical notes.\nPanel 1: a masked martial-arts warrior mid strike. Panel 2: a caped swordsman leaping. Panel 3: an armored archer drawing a bow. Panel 4: a staff-wielding monk in a spinning kick.\nUse restrained color accents only for energy veins, motion paths and symbolic highlights. Base material mostly ivory stone, gray marble, plaster dust, black ink, with faded red, muted blue, ochre, and small neon cracks. The composition feels like a sacred sports shrine, manga battle study, and museum artifact fused into one. Heroic poster-monument aesthetic, marble-carved, annotated like a legend, exploding with frozen action energy.",
