      "prompt": "Combined a bunch of ideas for this voxel manga scene: \n\nPrompt: \n2x2 grid, 16:9, do this for 4 famous mangas: { \"Scene_Type\": \"Macro Photography of an Open Magazine Spread\", \"Topic\": \"[FRANCHISE] - [SCENE]\", \"AI_Semantic_Inference\": { \"The_Pop_Up\": \"A 3D, isometric, highly detailed voxel/clay block of the [SCENE] rising out of the glossy magazine pages.\", \"The_Layout\": \"Left and Right margins feature editorial text columns, bold headlines, and 'Secret Stats' boxes.\", \"The_Callouts\": \"Red circles drawn around AI_INFER(hidden easter eggs in the 3D model), with red lines connecting them to the 2D margin text.\" }, \"Aesthetic\": \"Slightly glossy paper texture, vibrant colors, satisfying tactile blend of 2D print media and 3D isometric art.\" }",
      "prompt_ko": "[FRANCHISE]-[SCENE]를 넣으면 유명 만화 씬을 잡지 스프레드 매크로 사진으로 생성하는 함수형 JSON 템플릿(Gdgtify). 2x2 그리드 16:9. 각 패널=펼친 잡지 스프레드 매크로 촬영, [씬]의 3D 아이소메트릭 복셀/클레이 블록이 광택 잡지 페이지에서 튀어나옴, 좌우 여백에 에디토리얼 텍스트 칼럼·볼드 헤드라인·'Secret Stats' 박스, 3D 모델 속 숨은 이스터에그에 빨간 원 + 빨간 선으로 2D 여백 텍스트 연결. 약간 광택 종이 질감, 비비드 컬러, 2D 인쇄물+3D 아이소메트릭의 촉각적 블렌드. ★[FRANCHISE] IP는 오리지널 씬 4종으로 대체(저작권 회피).",
      "gen_prompt": "A 2x2 grid, 16:9, four macro photographs of open magazine spreads, each featuring a different original action scene (original characters and worlds only, no real franchise). For each panel: a 3D isometric highly detailed voxel / clay block of the scene rising out of the glossy magazine pages; left and right margins with editorial text columns, bold headlines and 'Secret Stats' boxes; red circles drawn around hidden easter eggs in the 3D model with thin red lines connecting them to the 2D margin text. Panel 1: a voxel ninja duel on a rooftop. Panel 2: a voxel mecha robot mid-launch. Panel 3: a voxel fantasy knight versus a dragon. Panel 4: a voxel street-racer drifting a car. Slightly glossy paper texture, vibrant colors, satisfying tactile blend of 2D print media and 3D isometric art, clean 2x2 grid composition.",
