      "prompt": "Nana banana pro promotional and Cinematic Prompt🏢 ⤵️\n\nA hyper-realistic editorial photo taken from a low angle looking up at a massive glass skyscraper in a busy urban city center. A gigantic [PRODUCT FROM UPLOADED IMAGE] is stuck directly onto the glass facade of the building. Two large strips of grey duct tape are placed ON TOP of the product itself crossing over it in an X shape, pressing it against the glass wall, the tape overlaps and covers parts of the product's packaging/label. The product is enormous in scale — nearly as wide as several floors of the building. The tape is visibly sticky, slightly wrinkled and reflective, casting a shadow on the product underneath. Crowds of people on the street below are looking up in shock and amusement, some filming with their smartphones. Glass skyscrapers reflect in the background, blue sky with light clouds above. Shot with a wide angle lens, slight fisheye distortion from the low perspective. Photorealistic, cinematic, natural daylight, urban atmosphere, candid crowd reaction. Use the exact product from the uploaded reference image — keep its original packaging, colors, logo, and shape.\n\nModel: Nano banana pro \n\n #HiggsfieldSoul2 #NanoBananaPro",
      "prompt_ko": "업로드한 제품을 초대형으로 확대해 도심 유리 마천루 외벽에 덕트테이프 X자로 붙인 초현실 시네마틱 광고(Maddox_Digital, Nano Banana Pro). 로우앵글로 마천루를 올려다보는 하이퍼리얼 에디토리얼 사진, 회색 덕트테이프 두 줄이 제품 위로 X자 교차하며 유리벽에 압착(테이프가 패키지 일부 덮음), 제품은 건물 여러 층 폭만큼 거대, 끈적·주름·반사 테이프가 그림자 드리움. 아래 거리 군중이 충격·재미로 올려다보며 스마트폰 촬영, 배경 유리 마천루 반사, 맑은 하늘. 와이드앵글·약한 피시아이 왜곡·포토리얼·시네마틱·자연광·도심 분위기·자연스러운 군중 반응. ★참조 제품 이미지 업로드가 전제(원 패키지·색·로고·형태 유지). gen_prompt는 오리지널 제품(에너지드링크 캔)으로 대체.",
      "gen_prompt": "A hyper-realistic editorial photo from a low angle looking up at a massive glass skyscraper in a busy urban city center. A gigantic colorful energy-drink can is stuck directly onto the glass facade of the building. Two large strips of grey duct tape are placed on top of the can, crossing over it in an X shape, pressing it against the glass wall; the tape overlaps and covers part of the can's label. The can is enormous in scale, nearly as wide as several floors of the building. The tape is visibly sticky, slightly wrinkled and reflective, casting a shadow on the can underneath. Crowds of people on the street below look up in shock and amusement, some filming with their smartphones. Glass skyscrapers reflect in the background, blue sky with light clouds above. Shot with a wide-angle lens, slight fisheye distortion from the low perspective. Photorealistic, cinematic, natural daylight, urban atmosphere, candid crowd reaction.",
