      "prompt": "رتّب الفوضى وابدأ الإبداع\n\nالبرومبت ⤵️\n\nCreate a premium cinematic advertising scene where [PRODUCT] transforms complete chaos into perfect order. Scattered elements related to the product float randomly, then are pulled toward [PRODUCT] and align into clean, elegant layouts and symmetrical compositions. Adapt the elements to the product type. Cinematic lighting, glowing particles, dynamic motion, realistic reflections, ultra-photorealistic, luxury commercial style, no people, no text, no watermark.",
