      "prompt": "Prompt:\n\nSurreal sports editorial photograph, soccer. Extreme fisheye wide-angle lens, dramatic low worm's-eye-view angle looking straight up. An athlete mid-air kicking, foot and boot impossibly enlarged and thrust toward camera, filling the frame with exaggerated forced perspective. Stadium background bends unnaturally like a warped diorama set. Shot on 35mm film camera, visible film grain, halation effect, muted cinematic color grading, soft desaturated tones, filmic contrast, no strong vignette, no black borders. Completely unbranded kit and equipment, generic, no logos, no brand marks, no text.",
      "prompt_ko": "초현실 스포츠 에디토리얼 사진(축구) — Seedream 5.0 PRO(Magnific). 극단 피시아이 와이드앵글, 드라마틱한 로우 웜아이뷰(벌레눈)로 정면 위를 올려다봄. 공중에서 킥하는 선수, 발과 부츠가 비현실적으로 확대돼 카메라로 돌출하며 과장된 강제원근으로 프레임을 채움. 경기장 배경이 뒤틀린 디오라마 세트처럼 부자연스럽게 휨. 35mm 필름 촬영, 필름 그레인, 헐레이션, 뮤티드 시네마틱 컬러그레이딩, 소프트 디새추레이트, 필름 콘트라스트, 강한 비네트 없음, 검은 테두리 없음. 완전 언브랜디드(로고·브랜드마크·텍스트 없음). ★구체적이라 gen_prompt=원문 그대로.",
      "gen_prompt": "Surreal sports editorial photograph, soccer. Extreme fisheye wide-angle lens, dramatic low worm's-eye-view angle looking straight up. An athlete mid-air kicking, foot and boot impossibly enlarged and thrust toward camera, filling the frame with exaggerated forced perspective. Stadium background bends unnaturally like a warped diorama set. Shot on 35mm film camera, visible film grain, halation effect, muted cinematic color grading, soft desaturated tones, filmic contrast, no strong vignette, no black borders. Completely unbranded kit and equipment, generic, no logos, no brand marks, no text.",
