      "category": "미니어처/그리드",
      "title": "캔디클레이 디자이너토이 팝월드 (함수형 $SUBJECT, 3컨셉 앵커 융합)",
      "prompt": "A pretty cute style for all kinds of topics. I used it for a world cup team.\n\nPrompt: \ndo this for France 2026 world cup team, CONCEPT ANCHOR 1: \"Candy-clay designer toy scene — rounded matte forms, soft vinyl surfaces, chunky plants, cute characters, pastel studio lighting\"   ::  CONCEPT ANCHOR 2: \"Bright editorial pop illustration — flat graphic colors, yellow backgrounds, green landscapes, red accents, playful city/world compositions\"  ::  CONCEPT ANCHOR 3: \"Miniature whimsical diorama — tiny houses, trees, props, stylized figures, toy-scale environments, clean staged presentation\"  INSTRUCTION: Find the exact visual center of these three concepts. Ignore the literal deer, houses, coffee, portraits, or landscapes. Capture only the material and composition logic.  Render $ SUBJECT as a bright collectible pop-world made from soft clay and graphic illustration.  STYLE RULES: - Convert the subject into rounded matte toy forms with smooth clay-like surfaces. - Use a joyful flat color system: lemon yellow, coral red, mint green, teal, warm orange, cream, bubblegum pink. - Build the world around the subject as a small toy-scale scene with tiny props, simplified plants, buildings, icons, and playful background shapes. - Use flat editorial composition with bold color blocking, graphic clouds, dots, squiggles, and decorative marks. - Keep the subject readable at a glance, but fill the scene with charming handcrafted details. - Avoid realism; everything should feel like a polished designer-toy illustration photographed or rendered for a trendy magazine cover.  OUTPUT: A joyful pop-clay world poster where $ SUBJECT becomes a cute, graphic, tactile collectible universe.",
      "prompt_ko": "$ SUBJECT를 소프트 클레이+그래픽 일러스트의 밝은 수집형 팝월드로 렌더링하는 함수형 템플릿(Gdgtify, 예시=France 2026 월드컵 팀). 3개 컨셉 앵커(①캔디클레이 디자이너토이 씬[둥근 매트 폼·소프트 비닐 표면·통통한 식물·귀여운 캐릭터·파스텔 스튜디오 조명] ②밝은 에디토리얼 팝 일러스트[플랫 그래픽 컬러·노란 배경·초록 풍경·빨강 액센트·경쾌한 도시/월드 구성] ③미니어처 위믹시컬 디오라마[작은 집·나무·소품·양식화 피규어·토이 스케일])의 시각 중심 추출. 스타일=둥근 매트 토이 폼·클레이 표면, 경쾌한 플랫 컬러(레몬옐로·코랄레드·민트그린·틸·웜오렌지·크림·버블검핑크). ★제이크 메모: 이 스타일을 다른 행사(GK 행사 등)로 치환 가능. gen_prompt=오리지널 스포츠 페스티벌 마스코트 팀 데모.",
      "gen_prompt": "Render an original friendly international sports-festival mascot squad as a bright collectible pop-world made from soft clay and graphic illustration. Convert the subjects into rounded matte toy forms with smooth clay-like vinyl surfaces, chunky stylized plants and props around them. Use a joyful flat color system: lemon yellow, coral red, mint green, teal, warm orange, cream, bubblegum pink. Build the world as a charming staged diorama — tiny stadium, little flags, toy trophies, cute rounded characters in team outfits, pastel studio lighting, clean collectible presentation, bright editorial pop-illustration backdrop with flat graphic color fields. Whimsical, cute, premium designer-toy aesthetic, soft shadows, satisfying tactile clay materials.",
