      "prompt": "GPT IMAGE 2 on CHATGPT \n\nPROMPT:\n\nSurreal minimalist collage poster on a solid dark [COLOR] background, featuring a torn black-and-white photograph of [HUMAN] wearing [CLOTHING] placed inside a rough paper frame. Add [LETTER, OR SHOPPLIST, BILL, ETC] behind the photo, [GRAPHIC ELEMENT] across the composition, and bold title text “[TITLE]” in a small block near the lower right. Use [COLOR PALETTE], ripped edges, tape marks, handwritten fragments, grainy photocopy texture, asymmetrical layout, strong negative space, raw editorial mood, sharp geometric contrast, handmade zine aesthetic, vertical 4:5.",
      "prompt_ko": "초현실 미니멀 콜라주 포스터 함수형 템플릿(SimplyAnnisa). 솔리드 다크 [COLOR] 배경에 [CLOTHING]을 입은 [HUMAN]의 찢은 흑백사진을 거친 종이 프레임 안에 배치, 사진 뒤에 [편지/장보기목록/영수증 등], 화면 전체에 [그래픽 요소], 우하단 작은 블록에 볼드 타이틀 '[TITLE]'. [컬러 팔레트]·찢긴 엣지·테이프 자국·손글씨 조각·거친 복사기 그레인 질감·비대칭 레이아웃·강한 여백·날것 에디토리얼 무드·샤프한 기하 대비·핸드메이드 zine 미학, 세로 4:5. ★함수형이라 대괄호를 구체값으로 치환. gen_prompt=다크틸+트렌치코트 인물 'SILENCE' 데모.",
      "gen_prompt": "Surreal minimalist collage poster on a solid dark teal background, featuring a torn black-and-white photograph of a pensive young woman wearing a vintage trench coat placed inside a rough paper frame. Add a faded handwritten letter behind the photo, a bold red geometric circle and thin crossing lines across the composition, and bold title text 'SILENCE' in a small block near the lower right. Use a limited palette of dark teal, cream, black and one red accent, ripped edges, tape marks, handwritten fragments, grainy photocopy texture, asymmetrical layout, strong negative space, raw editorial mood, sharp geometric contrast, handmade zine aesthetic, vertical 4:5.",
