      "target_model": "GPT Image 2 (ChatGPT) — 함수형 [TOPIC] 템플릿",
      "category": "스케일 인포그래픽",
      "title": "통계 분해 아이소메트릭 컷어웨이 (헤드라인 숫자 → 내부 컴포넌트 통계, 함수형 [TOPIC])",
      "prompt": "For the longest time, I used books and manga to test my  prompts. Turns out stats are also great for these types of experiments. This is a more normal looking prompt. \n\nPrompt: \nCreate a layered isometric 3D visualization that reveals how one large statistic about [TOPIC] is composed of smaller hidden statistics. The AI should choose one headline number, then break it into three to five meaningful components that explain where it comes from.\n\nRepresent the headline statistic as one large physical object: a tower, sphere, cube, machine, reservoir, mountain, or container. Cut away sections of the object to reveal nested chambers, materials, miniature scenes, or internal structures corresponding to the component metrics.\n\nFor example, a total cost might contain labor, materials, energy, logistics, and waste; total attention might contain watching, scrolling, searching, messaging, and waiting; total emissions might contain manufacturing, transport, use, and disposal.\n\nThe viewer should understand both the shocking total and its internal anatomy at a glance. Use restrained labels, small percentages, and one clear visual hierarchy. Include a familiar comparison object for scale only when useful.\n\nStyle: museum-grade isometric cutaway, matte clay and translucent materials, neutral concrete-grey background, soft lighting, precise ambient shadows. One oversized numeral should identify the total, while smaller numerals label the internal parts. Caption should state the metric, breakdown, timeframe, and source year.\n\nThe spirit: turn one statistic into a world that contains other statistics.",
      "prompt_ko": "[TOPIC]에 관한 하나의 큰 통계가 더 작은 숨은 통계들로 어떻게 구성되는지 드러내는 레이어드 아이소메트릭 3D 컷어웨이 시각화 함수형 템플릿(Gdgtify). AI가 헤드라인 숫자 하나를 고르고 그것을 3~5개의 의미있는 컴포넌트로 분해. 헤드라인 통계를 하나의 큰 물리 오브젝트(타워·구·큐브·기계·저수조·산·컨테이너)로 표현하고, 단면을 잘라내 컴포넌트 지표에 대응하는 중첩 챔버·소재·미니어처 씬·내부 구조를 드러냄. 예: 총비용=노동+재료+에너지+물류+폐기물 / 총주의=시청+스크롤+검색+메시지+대기 / 총배출=제조+운송+사용+폐기. 관람자가 충격적 총합과 내부 해부를 한눈에 이해. 절제된 라벨·작은 퍼센트·명확한 위계, 스케일용 익숙한 비교 오브젝트(유용할 때만). 스타일=뮤지엄급 아이소메트릭 컷어웨이·매트 클레이+반투명 소재·중립 콘크리트그레이 배경·부드러운 조명·정밀 앰비언트 섀도, 대형 숫자=총합, 작은 숫자=내부 파트. ★함수형이라 [TOPIC] 치환. gen_prompt=일일 스크린타임 데모.",
      "gen_prompt": "A layered isometric 3D cutaway visualization revealing how one large statistic — total daily screen time — is composed of smaller hidden statistics. Represent the headline statistic as one large physical object: a tall translucent glass reservoir tower. Cut away sections of the tower to reveal nested internal chambers corresponding to component metrics — watching, scrolling, searching, messaging, and waiting — each chamber a small miniature scene with its own material and color. One oversized numeral identifies the total number of hours, while smaller numerals label the internal parts with small percentages. Museum-grade isometric cutaway, matte clay and translucent glass materials, neutral concrete-grey background, soft museum lighting, precise ambient shadows, restrained labels, one clear visual hierarchy, a small familiar comparison object for scale.",
