      "title": "Exploded Layers 순수 제품 비주얼 (수직 분해, 텍스트·포스터 요소 없는 클린 제품샷)",
      "prompt": "Create a premium commercial product visual for the Orbitkey Key Organiser, presented using an exploded layers execution.\n\nShow one Orbitkey Key Organiser disassembled into its real functional components, floating in perfect vertical alignment: the leather outer strap, locking mechanism, metal post, washers, spacers, keys, internal hardware, and base components. Every layer should feel intentionally positioned, revealing how the product is engineered and assembled.\n\nUse a minimal dark studio environment with a deep charcoal-to-black background, warm brown leather, brushed metallic details, soft cinematic rim lighting, controlled reflections, realistic contact shadows, and subtle depth of field. The composition should feel luxurious, precise, intelligent, and editorial—like a premium industrial-design campaign.\n\nKeep the product anatomically believable and mechanically coherent. Maintain consistent scale, spacing, perspective, and material realism across all components.\n\nOne standalone image only. No grid, no collage, no comparison layout, no miniature scene, no micro-world, no micro-monument, no floating text, no labels, no infographic arrows, no extra objects, no duplicated components, no distorted keys, no invented mechanisms, and no advertising copy inside the image.\n\nUltra-detailed premium product photography, photorealistic materials, sophisticated art direction, precision engineering aesthetic, high-end commercial lighting.",
      "prompt_ko": "제품을 exploded layers(분해 레이어)로 수직 정렬 부유시킨 프리미엄 순수 제품 비주얼 프롬프트(aziz4ai, 예시=Orbitkey 키오거나이저). 제품을 실제 기능 컴포넌트(가죽 스트랩·잠금 기구·메탈 포스트·와셔·스페이서·키·내부 하드웨어·베이스)로 분해해 완벽한 수직 정렬로 부유, 각 레이어가 의도적으로 배치돼 제품 설계·조립 방식 드러냄. 미니멀 다크 스튜디오(차콜→블랙 배경)·웜 브라운 가죽·브러시드 메탈·소프트 시네마틱 림라이트·제어된 반사·리얼 접촉 그림자·얕은 심도. 럭셔리·정밀·에디토리얼, 프리미엄 산업디자인 캠페인 느낌. 기계적 정합성·일관 스케일·소재 리얼리즘. ★단일 클린 이미지 — 그리드·콜라주·라벨·인포그래픽 화살표·광고 카피 전부 배제(기존 [[aziz-1]] 'exploded-view 광고 포스터'와 달리 텍스트/포스터 요소 없는 순수 제품샷이 차별점). gen_prompt=제네릭 가죽 키오거나이저(브랜드명 제거).",
      "gen_prompt": "Create a premium commercial product visual of a leather key organiser, presented using an exploded-layers execution. Show the key organiser disassembled into its real functional components, floating in perfect vertical alignment: the leather outer strap, the locking mechanism, a metal post, washers, spacers, keys, internal hardware, and base components. Every layer intentionally positioned, revealing how the product is engineered and assembled. A minimal dark studio environment with a deep charcoal-to-black background, warm brown leather, brushed metallic details, soft cinematic rim lighting, controlled reflections, realistic contact shadows, and subtle depth of field. The composition feels luxurious, precise, intelligent and editorial, like a premium industrial-design campaign. Anatomically believable and mechanically coherent, consistent scale, spacing, perspective and material realism across all components. One standalone image only, no grid, no collage, no labels, no infographic arrows, no floating text, no advertising copy. Ultra-detailed premium product photography, photorealistic materials, sophisticated art direction.",
      "result": "results/aziz4ai-exploded-layers-clean-product-visual.png",
