      "prompt": "I spend so much time on highly complex prompts for my AI agents but if I were to write them for humans, they'd be much shorter and readable 😅 Here is one for philosophers: \n\n2x2 grid, 16:9, do this for 4 famous philosophers; graphic design poster, bauhaus aesthetic, [geometrically abstract $ subject figure in a rigid pose, showing structural order or chaotic dissent], [subtle backdrop of intersecting primary-colored circles and triangles], functionalist art style, vector art, flat 2d rendering, strong grid composition, sans-serif typography aesthetic, high resolution, design museum archive quality, 1920s avant-garde documentation, modernist gallery showcase",
      "prompt_ko": "유명 철학자를 바우하우스 그래픽 디자인 포스터로 만드는 gdgtify 함수형 템플릿(사람용으로 짧고 읽기 쉽게 작성). 2x2 그리드 16:9, 4명 철학자. 각 패널=기하학적으로 추상화된 $subject figure가 경직된 포즈로 구조적 질서 또는 혼돈적 반체제를 표현, 교차하는 원색(빨강/파랑/노랑) 원·삼각형의 은은한 배경. 기능주의 아트 스타일·벡터 아트·플랫 2D·강한 그리드 구성·산세리프 타이포 미학·디자인 뮤지엄 아카이브급·1920s 아방가르드 다큐멘테이션·모더니스트 갤러리 쇼케이스. ★특정 실존인물 대신 오리지널 추상 figure로 처리.",
      "gen_prompt": "A 2x2 grid, 16:9, of four original abstract philosopher figures rendered as Bauhaus graphic-design posters. Each panel: a geometrically abstract figure in a rigid pose showing structural order or chaotic dissent, over a subtle backdrop of intersecting primary-colored circles and triangles. Functionalist art style, vector art, flat 2D rendering, strong grid composition, sans-serif typographic aesthetic, high resolution, design-museum archive quality, 1920s avant-garde documentation, modernist gallery showcase. Original abstract characters, no specific real person, clean 2x2 grid with thin gutters.",
