      "title": "럭셔리 시계 운석 폭발 캠페인 포스터 (딥블루 일렉트릭 글로우, 중앙 히어로)",
      "prompt": "✨The blue electric glow takes the machine's cold, mechanical feel to the extreme\n蓝色电光把机械的冷感推到极致\n\nGPT- image 2 prompt👇\nCreate a single-image luxury campaign poster for Vacheron Constantin Overseas 4500V, built around an intense deep-blue meteor eruption scene. The composition is vertical, clean, minimal, and highly focused: one monumental watch dominates the exact center of the frame, suspended between two fractured dark meteor stones, one floating above and one below, both split open to reveal blinding electric-blue inner energy, liquid plasma light, and crystalline mineral glow.\n\nThe Vacheron Constantin Overseas 4500V must remain the absolute hero object, rendered with ultra-premium realism, perfect proportions, razor-sharp craftsmanship, brushed and polished stainless steel surfaces, a rich blue dial, and highly refined sapphire reflections. The watch should feel physically fused into the environment, as if born from the meteor energy itself. Reflections across the bezel, crystal, dial, case edges, and bracelet must accurately capture the same blue inner glow, suspended mineral dust, and exploding fragments from the surrounding stones.\n\nThe upper meteor is massive, dark, rugged, and heavy, with a cracked underside radiating intense blue molten light. The lower meteor acts like a fractured pedestal, cradling the watch from below while emitting liquid-like luminous energy that spreads outward in a controlled, realistic burst. A few smaller floating meteor fragments orbit the watch in balanced positions, helping build a sense of tension and dimensionality without cluttering the frame. Fine glowing particles, cold blue dust, and subtle atmospheric debris are suspended in the surrounding darkness.\n\nThe background must be minimal and cinematic: deep navy-black, abyssal, spacious, with faint blue haze, delicate floating particles, and soft volumetric diffusion. No busy environment, no extra scenery, no collage layout. The entire image should feel like a frozen celestial impact moment, highly disciplined, premium, and visually explosive while remaining elegant and clean.\n\nTypography should be minimal and integrated if present: a refined, thin, luxury editorial text treatment placed subtly into the negative space, such as “OVERSEAS” and “VACHERON CONSTANTIN”, with small supporting campaign text kept understated and spatially embedded. No heavy fonts, no bold commercial clutter, no cheap sci-fi styling.\n\nLighting: ultra-controlled luxury product lighting, electric sapphire-blue highlights, cold metallic reflections, deep shadow contrast, luminous plasma bloom inside the meteor cracks, crisp steel speculars, highly realistic sapphire crystal behavior, museum-grade watch photography.\n\nMood: mysterious, explosive, abyssal, powerful, ultra-luxury, cosmic, disciplined, and immersive.\n\nRendering style: hyper-realistic commercial watch photography, premium campaign poster aesthetic, extreme material fidelity, realistic fractured mineral surfaces, cinematic micro-contrast, immaculate retouching, 8k, sharp but elegant, high-end editorial finish.\n\nNegative prompt: cartoon, fantasy illustration, oversized visual effects, messy composition, multiple panels, cluttered background, cheap neon glow, distorted watch anatomy, low-detail bracelet, fake reflections, soft muddy metal, generic sci-fi poster, rough typography, low-end ad feeling",
      "prompt_ko": "럭셔리 시계를 강렬한 딥블루 운석 폭발 씬으로 감싼 단일 캠페인 포스터(ou_zhen599, 원본 예시=Vacheron Constantin Overseas 4500V). 세로·클린·미니멀·고집중 구성: 하나의 기념비적 시계가 프레임 정중앙 지배, 위아래로 갈라진 어두운 운석 두 덩이 사이에 부유(위 하나·아래 하나), 둘 다 쪼개져 눈부신 일렉트릭 블루 내부 에너지·리퀴드 플라즈마 광·결정질 미네랄 글로우 노출. 시계=절대 히어로 오브젝트(울트라 프리미엄 리얼리즘·완벽 비율·예리한 크래프트맨십·브러시드+폴리시드 스테인리스·리치 블루 다이얼·정제된 사파이어 반사, 운석 에너지에서 태어난 듯 환경에 물리적 융합). 베젤·크리스털·다이얼·케이스 엣지·브레이슬릿 반사가 동일 블루 내부 광·부유 미네랄 먼지·폭발 파편 정확 포착. 딥 니어블랙 배경·볼류메트릭 블루 글로우·시네마틱 럭셔리 광고. ★브랜드는 오리지널 프리미엄 스포츠 시계로 대체(저작권). 원문 3.4k자 압축(gen_prompt).",
      "gen_prompt": "A single-image luxury campaign poster for an original premium stainless-steel sports watch with a rich blue dial, built around an intense deep-blue meteor eruption scene. Vertical, clean, minimal, highly focused: one monumental watch dominates the exact center of the frame, suspended between two fractured dark meteor stones — one floating above and one below — both split open to reveal blinding electric-blue inner energy, liquid plasma light, and crystalline mineral glow. The watch is the absolute hero object, rendered with ultra-premium realism, perfect proportions, razor-sharp craftsmanship, brushed and polished stainless-steel surfaces, a rich blue dial, and refined sapphire reflections, as if born from the meteor energy itself. Reflections across the bezel, crystal, dial, case edges and bracelet accurately capture the same blue inner glow, suspended mineral dust and exploding fragments from the surrounding stones. The upper meteor is massive, dark and rugged, cracked open with electric-blue plasma veins; the lower stone echoes it. Deep near-black background, volumetric blue glow, floating mineral particles, cinematic luxury advertising, ultra-detailed, dramatic rim light, razor-sharp product focus, no brand logo.",
