      "category": "매거진 커버",
      "title": "애니 캐릭터 타이포 관통 에디토리얼 매거진 커버 (얼굴이 대형 글자 사이로, 함수형)",
      "prompt": "GPT IMAGE 2 on CHATGPT \n\nCreate a premium minimalist editorial magazine cover featuring [CHARACTER] from [SERIES]. The portrait should be a highly detailed anime illustration with painterly textures, soft cinematic lighting, realistic shading, sharp facial features, and an intense expression. The character fills the entire page while being partially revealed through oversized bold geometric sans-serif typography spanning the cover, with the face perfectly aligned across the letter cutouts. Use a clean black-and-white editorial layout with generous negative space, thick white dividers, rounded grid intersections, modern Swiss-inspired typography, magazine branding at the top, issue number, barcode, Japanese vertical text, English captions, small logos, quotes, publication details, and subtle print paper texture. High-end fashion magazine aesthetic, luxury graphic design, balanced composition, muted color palette matching the character, ultra-sharp, premium print quality, contemporary visual culture publication, 4:5 aspect ratio.",
      "prompt_ko": "애니 캐릭터를 대형 타이포가 관통하는 프리미엄 미니멀 에디토리얼 매거진 커버 함수형 템플릿(SimplyAnnisa). [CHARACTER] from [SERIES]. 고디테일 애니 일러스트(페인터리 질감·소프트 시네마틱 조명·리얼 셰이딩·샤프한 이목구비·강렬한 표정), 캐릭터가 페이지 전체를 채우되 ★커버를 가로지르는 초대형 볼드 기하 산세리프 타이포에 부분적으로 가려지고, 얼굴이 글자 컷아웃(글자 사이 빈 공간)에 완벽히 정렬돼 글자 틈으로 보임. 클린 흑백 에디토리얼 레이아웃·넉넉한 여백·두꺼운 흰 디바이더·라운드 그리드 교차·모던 스위스 타이포·상단 매거진 브랜딩·이슈번호·바코드·일본어 세로 텍스트·영문 캡션·소형 로고·인용·발행정보·미묘한 인쇄 종이 질감. 하이엔드 패션 매거진 미학·럭셔리 그래픽·뮤티드 팔레트(캐릭터에 맞춤)·울트라 샤프·4:5. ★IP 캐릭터는 오리지널 애니 인물로 대체. ★재현 관건=타이포 글자 사이 얼굴 정렬(제이크 재현테스트 요청).",
      "gen_prompt": "Create a premium minimalist editorial magazine cover featuring an original anime warrior girl character with sharp facial features and an intense expression. Highly detailed anime illustration with painterly textures, soft cinematic lighting, realistic shading. The character fills the entire page while being partially revealed through oversized bold geometric sans-serif typography spanning the cover — large letters reading 'AXIS' — with the face perfectly aligned across the letter cutouts so the face shows through the gaps between the letters. Clean black-and-white editorial layout with generous negative space, thick white dividers, rounded grid intersections, modern Swiss-inspired typography, magazine branding at the top, an issue number, a barcode, small Japanese vertical text, English captions, small logos, quotes, publication details, and subtle print paper texture. High-end fashion magazine aesthetic, luxury graphic design, balanced composition, muted color palette matching the character, ultra-sharp, premium print quality, 4:5 aspect ratio.",
