      "prompt": "This SREF feels like a sun-faded poster from a stylish little design shop in the 70s, rebuilt with clean modern geometry.\n\n--sref 3005315149 --v 6.1 --sv4\n\nThink coral reds, soft pinks, leafy greens, delicate line art, flat shapes, and that subtle screen-printed texture that makes digital work feel handmade.\n\nIt’s minimal, but not cold.\nRetro, but not outdated.\nDecorative, but still clean enough for modern branding.\n\nThis style works beautifully for:\nboutique packaging\nlifestyle magazine illustrations\nfashion campaign posters\nhome decor prints\ncoffee shop branding\nsocial media visuals\nart-forward product ads\n\nIf you want the image to feel warmer and more tactile, add keywords like line art, texture overlay, screen print, handcrafted illustration, or Mondrian palette.\n\nI dropped the full prompt in the comments so you can test and recreate this exact style. #midjourney #sref",
      "prompt_ko": "미드저니 sref 3005315149 스타일 카드(@promptsref) — 70s 세련된 디자인샵의 색바랜 포스터를 클린 모던 지오메트리로 재구축한 느낌. ★--sref 코드 이식 불가 + 실제 프롬프트 외부(유료) 게이트 → 원본 이미지 스타일 직접 분석해 자연어 재구성. 스타일=코랄레드·소프트핑크·리프그린 팔레트·섬세한 흰 라인아트·플랫 셰이프·미묘한 스크린프린트 텍스처·종이 색바램. 2x2 예시=라인아트 붉은 물고기·라인 텍스처 붉은머리 천사·핑크톤 레트로 도시 스카이라인·핑크 배경 몬스테라 잎. 원본 비교탭 등록. ★70s 디자인샵 스크린프린트 미학.",
      "gen_prompt": "A 2x2 grid in the style of a sun-faded poster from a stylish 1970s design shop, rebuilt with clean modern geometry. Coral reds, soft pinks and leafy greens, delicate fine white line art, flat shapes, subtle screen-printed texture and paper fading.\nPanel 1: a stylized red goldfish rendered in flat shapes with fine white contour lines on a dark panel with rounded retro stripes.\nPanel 2: a serene red-haired winged figure resting her head on her hand, her body covered in delicate line-art contours, warm coral-and-cream palette on faded paper.\nPanel 3: a pink-toned retro city skyline at golden hour in flat screen-print shapes.\nPanel 4: large deep-green monstera leaves against a soft pink screen-printed background with a fine grid texture.\n70s design-shop poster aesthetic, coral / pink / green palette, delicate line art, flat vector shapes, screen-print grain, sun-bleached fading, clean 2x2 grid.",
