      "title": "미드센추리 빈티지 여행엽서 [DESTINATION] 템플릿 (볼드 보더+대형 크림 레트로 산세리프+플랫 지오메트릭 벡터, 1950-60s 스크린프린트)",
      "prompt": "Create a vintage mid-century travel postcard illustration of [DESTINATION] ([LOCAL NAME]), framed by a bold [BORDER COLOR] border with large cream uppercase retro sans-serif typography displaying the destination name and local name beneath it. Showcase the region's most iconic mountains, landmarks, wildlife, waterways, towns, flora, and cultural elements in a clean geometric vector style using flat shapes, sharp lines, and bold saturated colors. Include a bright sky with a stylized sun, scenic landscapes, small boats or vehicles, native plants and animals, and tiny people to add scale and life. Use a harmonious palette inspired by the destination, subtle vintage screen-print texture, balanced composition, and an authentic 1950s-1960s travel poster aesthetic. High detail, print-ready, crisp vector look, 4K.",
      "prompt_ko": "임의 여행지를 미드센추리 빈티지 여행엽서로 만드는 @noorwithwifi 영문 템플릿([DESTINATION]/[LOCAL NAME]/[BORDER COLOR] 치환형). 볼드 보더 프레임+대형 크림색 대문자 레트로 산세리프로 지명·현지명 표기. 그 지역 상징 산·랜드마크·야생동물·수로·마을·식생·문화요소를 플랫 셰이프·샤프 라인·볼드 채도 벡터로. 스타일라이즈드 태양·소형 보트·현지 동식물·작은 인물(스케일감). 여행지 파생 조화 팔레트+빈티지 스크린프린트 텍스처, 1950-60s 여행포스터 미학. gen_prompt=뉴질랜드(Aotearoa) 대표 데모.",
      "gen_prompt": "Create a vintage mid-century travel postcard illustration of New Zealand (Aotearoa), framed by a bold deep-teal border with large cream uppercase retro sans-serif typography displaying NEW ZEALAND and AOTEAROA beneath it. Showcase the region's most iconic mountains (the Southern Alps and Aoraki/Mount Cook), landmarks, wildlife (a kiwi bird), waterways, coastal towns, flora (silver fern), and Maori cultural elements in a clean geometric vector style using flat shapes, sharp lines, and bold saturated colors. Include a bright sky with a stylized sun, scenic fjord landscapes, small boats, native plants and animals, and tiny people to add scale and life. Use a harmonious palette inspired by New Zealand's greens and blues, subtle vintage screen-print texture, balanced composition, and an authentic 1950s-1960s travel poster aesthetic. High detail, print-ready, crisp vector look, 4K.",
