      "prompt": "History of earth visualized in a cute way. 2x2 grid, 16:9, do this 4 distinct epochs in earth's history -> style { A = { central subject: rounded sculptural clay/vinyl figure, chunky toy proportions } B = { pencil-sketch marks: black contour lines, doodle eyes, loose shading, construction marks } C = { pop-color accents: bright stickers, beads, confetti, decorative icons } D = { miniature playset: simplified buildings, soft hills, toy trees, clouds, signs } E = { background: colorful backdrop, poster-like separation } SCENE = (A intersect centerpiece) union (B intersect overlay) union (C intersect scattered) union (D intersect environment) union (E intersect backdrop) Where: - A is a smooth, rounded 3D object inferred from $SUBJECT, simplified into soft capsules and thick tubes. - B lines are generated from the silhouette and internal features; thicker on outer edges, lighter doodles inside. - C elements are placed in a Poisson-disk pattern around the figure, avoiding clutter. - D is kept low-height to frame the subject, with chunky blocks and toy plants. - E is a gradient from cream to bubblegum pink with soft clouds. All colors locked to the candy palette; black pencil is reserved for sketch marks only. }",
      "prompt_ko": "임의 주제($SUBJECT)를 귀여운 clay/vinyl 토이 2x2 그리드(16:9)로 만드는 @Gdgtify 함수형 집합표기 템플릿. A=둥근 조형 클레이/비닐 피규어(청키 토이 비율) B=연필스케치(흑색 컨투어·두들 눈·러프 셰이딩·작도선) C=팝컬러 액센트(스티커·비즈·컨페티·데코 아이콘, Poisson-disk 배치로 산만함 회피) D=미니어처 플레이셋(단순화 건물·언덕·토이 나무·구름·표지판, 낮게 깔아 주제 프레이밍) E=크림→버블검핑크 그라디언트 배경+부드러운 구름. 캔디 팔레트 고정, 흑색 연필은 스케치 마크 전용. gen_prompt=지구 4개 시대(하데안 용암/캄브리아 바다/쥐라기 공룡/빙하기 매머드) 구체화.",
      "gen_prompt": "A cute 2x2 grid, 16:9, showing four distinct epochs of Earth's history: top-left the Hadean molten early Earth with erupting volcanoes and lava rivers; top-right the Cambrian ocean with adorable trilobites and jellyfish; bottom-left the Jurassic age with a chunky toy dinosaur among giant ferns; bottom-right the Ice Age with a woolly mammoth in snow. Each panel rendered in the same style: a central rounded sculptural clay/vinyl figure with chunky toy proportions as the centerpiece; black pencil-sketch marks with contour lines, doodle eyes, loose shading and construction marks overlaid; pop-color accents like bright stickers, beads, confetti and decorative icons scattered in a Poisson-disk pattern avoiding clutter; a low miniature playset of simplified buildings, soft hills, toy trees, clouds and signs framing the subject; a colorful poster-like backdrop that is a gradient from cream to bubblegum pink with soft clouds. All colors locked to a candy palette; black pencil reserved for sketch marks only. Playful, editorial clay-toy diorama look.",
