      "gen_prompt": "A surreal crystalline world rendered as high-end sci-fi concept art: translucent faceted crystal formations and ethereal glowing sculptural structures floating in a deep, pure-black void; refractive glass-like surfaces catching prismatic light, soft inner luminescence, delicate iridescent reflections and caustics, a sense of something both real and impossible. Futuristic, clean, otherworldly, luxurious exhibition-poster mood. Ultra high detail, cinematic rim lighting, minimal composition with vast black negative space, crisp focus, 4K.",
